NK131(do)005:1: // sdom pa gsum gyi rab tu dbye ba'i bstan bcos
NK131(do)005:2: chen pos snga 'gyur phyogs la rtsod pa spong ba
NK131(do)005:3: 'dus ma byas kyi gan mdzod ces bya ba bzhugs
NK131(do)005:4: so // sdom pa gsum gyi rab tu dbye ba'i
NK131(do)005:5: bstan bcos chen pos snga 'gyur phyogs la rtsod pa
NK131(do)005:6: spong ba 'dus ma byas kyi gan mdzod ces bya
NK131(do)005:7: so // ba / dpal bla ma dang sangs rgyas la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK131(do)005:8: gang gi rang bzhin gdod nas rab zhi bas //
NK131(do)005:9: mtha' dag blo yi grub mthas ma reg pa'i //
NK131(do)005:10: chos rnams kun gyi chos nyid gang yin pa //
NK131(do)005:11: rdzogs pa chen po'i mtshan gyis bstan la 'dud //
NK131(do)005:12: tshig chus myos pa'i 'phrog byed glang po'i mgor //
NK131(do)005:13: lung dang rigs pa'i sder sen ngal bsos pas //
NK131(do)005:14: thub bstan kun dag'i rgyal matshana kee l+aa shar //
NK131(do)005:15: bslangs pa'i grags dkar srid pa gsum na 'phro //
NK131(do)005:16: de la chos kyi rje 'jam pa'i dbyangs sa skya
NK131(do)005:17: pan+di ta chen pos sdom pa gsum gyi rab tu
NK131(do)005:18: dbye ba'i bstan bcos 'di mdzad pa na log par
NK131(do)005:19: rtog pa'i skye bo dag gis skabs 'dir chos rje
NK131(do)005:20: sa skya pas rnying ma phyogs sngar mdzad nas bkag
NK131(do)005:21: go snyam pa'i log rtog rgya cher 'phel nas chos
NK131(do)005:22: dang gang zag mang po dri ma can du byas
NK131(do)005:23: so // de bas na bdag gis lhag bsam rnam
NK131(do)005:24: par dag pas kun nas bslangs te dri ma de
NK131(do)005:25: dag sel bar byed pa la gnyis /
NK131(do)005:26: bstan bcos mkhan po'i dgongs pa brtag pa dang /
NK131(do)005:27: gzhan gyi log rtog rnam par sel ba'o //
NK131(do)005:28: dang po ni gangs can yongs su grags pa'i rdzogs pa chen po dang /
NK131(do)005:30: yid la mi byed pa'i chos skor rnams dang /
NK131(do)005:31: byin rlabs brgyud pa'i bka' srol rnams dang /
NK131(do)005:32: byin rlabs 'pho ba'i rim pa dang /
NK131(do)005:33: dag snang dang snyan nas brgyud pa'i chos skor rnams dang /
NK131(do)005:34: gcig brgyud kyi rim pa 'doms pa'i bla ma'i man ngag rnams dang /
NK131(do)005:35: gsang sngags kyi zab don thun mong ma yin pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)005:36: don la rton pa'i bshad pa 'ga' zhig dang /
NK131(do)005:37: bskyed pa'i rim pa spros med dang /
NK131(do)005:38: mtshan ma med pa'i rdzogs rim zab mo 'ga' zhig
NK131(do)005:39: la bstan bcos 'di'i dngos bstan gyi tshig gis dpyad
NK131(do)005:40: gzhir mdzad pa shin tu mang mod kyi /
NK131(do)005:41: snga 'gyur phyogs su dpyad gzhir dogs pa nyung shas tsam las med la /
NK131(do)005:42: 'on kyang sa bon tsam de la brten nas 'ga'
NK131(do)005:43: zhig la log par rtog pa rgya cher 'phel zhing
NK131(do)005:44: / sdang sems kho nas rnying ma 'gog pa'i ming
NK131(do)005:45: tsam la dgyes pa lhur len pa po dag gis
NK131(do)005:46: bstan bcos mkhan po'i dgongs pa'i mthil ma rtogs shing
NK131(do)005:47: rab dbye'i dngos bstan gyi tshig don la dpyad pa
NK131(do)005:48: zhib mo tsam yang bya long med par /
NK131(do)005:49: skabs 'dir chos rje sa skya pas rnying ma bkag
NK131(do)005:50: go snyam du yid la byed cing tshig zur gyis
NK131(do)005:51: ltar snang du gang gnod par nus so snyam pa
NK131(do)005:52: thams cad rgyab rten du 'khyer ba zhig byung mod
NK131(do)005:53: kyang chu gcig gi mtshan nyid gsher bar shes pas
NK131(do)005:54: chu thams cad kyi mtshan nyid shes pa bzhin du
NK131(do)005:55: rjes 'brang gi rtsod pa thams cad ltar snang du
NK131(do)005:56: grub pa nyid shes sla bar zad do //
NK131(do)005:57: 'o na chos kyi rjes de ltar 'chad pa la dgos pa ci lta bu yod ce na /
NK131(do)005:59: bstan pa phyi dar gyi thog ma tshugs nas ring
NK131(do)005:60: por ma lon par mar mi'i bka' brgyud rin po
NK131(do)005:61: che byang phyogs 'dir 'gro ba'i bsod nams kyi dpal
NK131(do)005:62: du byon zhing / de las dwags po rin po
NK131(do)005:63: ches mdo ting rgyal sogs kyi dgongs pa theg pa
NK131(do)005:64: chen po rgyud bla ma'i dngos bstan gyi dgongs pa
NK131(do)005:65: phyin theg pa'i lam rim man ngag gis bkral ba'i
NK131(do)005:66: sher phyin la mtshan gzhan phyag rgya chen po btags
NK131(do)005:67: te thang brdal nas bstan pas las dang po la'ang
NK131(do)005:68: rang bzhin gnyug ma gzhi'i gnas lugs phyag rgya chen
NK131(do)005:69: po'i rtogs pa bskrun par mdzad pa de nyid byin
NK131(do)005:70: rlabs 'pho ba'i don gyi dbang bskur thog mar 'gro
NK131(do)005:71: ba'i thabs lam la brten nas sngags kyi phyag rgya
NK131(do)005:72: chen por bogs dbyung nas slob ma'i rgyud la ye
NK131(do)005:73: shes bskyed pas gangs can gyi ri'i sul thams cad
NK131(do)005:74: nges don sgrub brgyud kyi rgyal mtshan 'dzin pas bkang
NK131(do)005:75: zhing grub thob kyi tshang chen po rdol ba yin
NK131(do)005:76: du byon zhing / la / de dang dus mtshungs
NK131(do)005:77: par grub thob khyung chen po rnal 'byor gyis n+aa
NK131(do)005:78: ro'i lcam ni gu la rdo rje 'chang gis dngos
NK131(do)005:79: su bstan pa'i zab mo chos drug bod du bstan
NK131(do)005:80: pas lam de las kyang dngos grub brnyes pa du
NK131(do)005:81: du byon zhing / la / ma dang / dpal
NK131(do)005:82: ldan zur pa mes dbon gsum sogs mdo dang sgyu
NK131(do)005:83: 'phrul gyi lam la brten nas bsad pa gso bar
NK131(do)005:84: nus pa sogs thun mong gi las chen po rnams
NK131(do)005:86: mchog gi dngos grub dpal he ru ka dang dgongs
NK131(do)005:87: pa mnyam pas 'og min tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil
NK131(do)005:88: 'khor du sku lus de nyid kyis gshegs pa du
NK131(do)005:90: spa sgom sogs klong sde'i lam gyis rags pa'i lus rdul phran du dengs pa dang /
NK131(do)005:91: ldang ma dang lce btsun dang 'khrul zhig seng ge
NK131(do)005:92: rgyab pa sogs mngon sum snying thig gi lam nas
NK131(do)005:93: phung po 'od du dengs pa'ang shin tu mang bar
NK131(do)005:94: byon pas dus skabs de dag tu bod kyi gang
NK131(do)005:95: zag byings rnams lam de dang de la 'dun zhing
NK131(do)005:96: zhugs pa ha cang mang bas /
NK131(do)005:97: gong du brjod pa de dag gi don gyi gnas
NK131(do)005:98: la nor ba mi srid kyang tshig gi spros pa
NK131(do)005:99: dang phyag len cung zad zor yang du mdzad pas
NK131(do)005:100: mdo sngags thun mong pa'i shin rta chen po'i lugs
NK131(do)005:101: srol las bag tsam g.yel ba ltar gyur pa gzigs
NK131(do)005:102: nas chos kyi rje dpal ldan sa skya pa dus
NK131(do)005:103: skabs der gangs can gyi ljongs 'dir bstan pa'i bdag
NK131(do)005:104: por mthun snang du grub pas yongs su grags pa'i
NK131(do)005:105: gzhung lugs chen po rnams la thos bsam gyis 'jug
NK131(do)005:106: pa'i shing rta'i srol mi nyams pa la dgongs nas
NK131(do)005:107: rab dbye'i bstan bcos 'di nyid brtsams pa na /
NK131(do)005:108: grub mtha' la ma zhugs pa'i khyim pa phyogs lhung
NK131(do)005:109: can dag gis kyang rang gi glo ba gang la
NK131(do)005:110: byang ba de yi dam du byas nas gzhan skyon
NK131(do)005:111: can du bsgrub pa'i phyir bstan bcos 'di'i tshig rnams
NK131(do)005:112: kha ton du byed pa dang /
NK131(do)005:113: grub mtha' par khas 'che ba'i smra ba po dag
NK131(do)005:114: kyang 'ga' zhig ni rtog dpyod ma zhugs bzhin du
NK131(do)005:115: brag cha'i lad mo zlo ba dang /
NK131(do)005:116: 'ga' zhig ni 'ga' dang 'ga' la phrag dog gi
NK131(do)005:117: bsam pa sngon du btang nas bstan bcos mdzad pa
NK131(do)005:118: po'i dgongs pa ma lon pa'am lon yang rung phyogs
NK131(do)005:119: lhung gi 'og nas ldang bar ma nus pa'i rgyab
NK131(do)005:120: rten du 'di'i dngos bstan gyi tshig kho na skyor
NK131(do)005:121: zlos byas pas skal ba dman pa'i skye bo 'ga'
NK131(do)005:122: zhig chos spong ba la sbyar ba'i zhar du gzhung
NK131(do)005:123: 'di nyid kyang dri ma can du byas so //
NK131(do)005:125: bstan bcos kyi tshig la brten nas gzhan gyis dogs pa bslangs ba de dang /
NK131(do)005:126: de lung dang rigs pas sel bas so //
NK131(do)005:128: dngos su gsal ba'i dgag sgrub yod par 'dod pa dang /
NK131(do)005:129: zur gyis phog pa yod par 'dod pa sel ba'o //
NK131(do)005:131: dbu ma dang gsang sngags lta ba khyad par med par 'dod pa /
NK131(do)005:132: lta sgom shan ma phye bar 'dod pa /
NK131(do)005:133: rgyud sde gong ma gsum theg pa'i rim par mi 'dod pa'i skyon spong ngo //
NK131(do)005:136: pha rol phyin pa'i spros bral las //
NK131(do)005:137: lhag pa'i lta ba yod na ni //
NK131(do)005:138: lta de spros pa can du 'gyur //
NK131(do)005:139: spros bral yin na khyad par med //
NK131(do)005:141: chos kyi rjes stong nyid spros bral tsam la chos spyi'i lta bar bzhag pa'i gnas skabs gcig dang /
NK131(do)005:142: nyams myong de kho na nyid kyi ye shes la
NK131(do)005:143: gsang sngags thun mong ma yin pa'i lta bar bzhag
NK131(do)005:144: pa'i gnas skabs gnyis so sor bzhed pa ma rtogs
NK131(do)005:145: pa dang / phyis kyi rtog ge la ches goms
NK131(do)005:146: pa dag gis lta ba zhes pa'i tshig 'di la
NK131(do)005:147: brten nas mdo sngags gnyis ka'i lta ba gcig tu
NK131(do)005:148: pa dang / dpyad / des nyams myong gi ye
NK131(do)005:149: shes kyang med dgag gi spros bral tsam du bsam
NK131(do)005:150: pa dang / dpyad / / lta ba'i ming tsam
NK131(do)005:151: la brten nas dbang gi ye shes mngon sum nyams
NK131(do)005:152: su myong byar yod bzhin du rtog dpyod yan lag
NK131(do)005:153: tu dgos par 'dod pas rdo rje theg pa'i zab
NK131(do)005:154: gnad la cung zad bsgribs te rtog dpyod de lta
NK131(do)005:155: ba rtogs pa'i thabs yin pa la ma bsams so
NK131(do)005:156: pa dang / dpyad / / // de'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK131(do)005:157: spyir lta ba zhes pa rgyu'i theg pa pa'i spros
NK131(do)005:158: bral thos bsam gyi dpyad don kho nar ngos bzung
NK131(do)005:159: bas lan / de lta na rjes thob tu bsam
NK131(do)005:160: byung gis dpyad pa'i tshig tu mi 'dod ka med
NK131(do)005:161: bas lan / byung yang / mnyam gzhag gi gnas
NK131(do)005:162: skabs ni tshig dang sgra rtog gi yul yin pa
NK131(do)005:163: bas lan / byung yang / lta zhog / zhen
NK131(do)005:164: pa'i yul tsam yang ma yin par bzhed pa 'di
NK131(do)005:165: ni sngon gyi chen po rnams kyang mgrin gcig tu
NK131(do)005:166: bshad na de'i yul la lta ba'i gdams gzhi ma
NK131(do)005:167: grub ste khas blang thams cad dang bral bar bzhed
NK131(do)005:168: pa 'dir don gyis mi mthun pa med /
NK131(do)005:169: spyir blo'i yul du byas pa'i stong nyid de chos
NK131(do)005:170: nyid la rjes su dpag pa'i go yul tsam las
NK131(do)005:171: dngos po'i gnas lugs ma yin par gsungs te /
NK131(do)005:172: chos nyid don dam pa'i bden pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes dang /
NK131(do)005:173: klog pa thos bsam pa phal cher zhig gis /
NK131(do)005:174: ngo bo'i cha la 'dug tshul ji lta ba rgyud
NK131(do)005:175: la ma myong bzhin du tshig gi cha la rtog
NK131(do)005:176: dpyod kyis sgro btags pa'i blo'i yul du gyur pa'i
NK131(do)005:177: rtog dpyod kyi shes rab gnyis rdzas 'gal ba'i tshul
NK131(do)005:178: bcom ldan 'das kyis lan cig ma yin par gsungs
NK131(do)005:179: te / rdo rje gcod pa las kyang /
NK131(do)005:180: chos nyid shes bya ma yin te //
NK131(do)005:181: de ni rnam par shes mi nus //
NK131(do)005:183: drin lan bsab pa'i mdo las /
NK131(do)005:184: don la gnas kyi yi ge'i rjes su mi gnas /
NK131(do)005:185: ye shes la gnas kyi rnam par shes pa'i rjes su mi gnas /
NK131(do)005:186: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa dang /
NK131(do)005:188: don dam blo yi spyod yul min //
NK131(do)005:189: blo ni kun rdzob yin par 'dod //
NK131(do)005:190: ces gsungs pa 'di tsam gyis kyang shes par nus so //
NK131(do)005:191: 'o na thos bsam gyis rtogs par bshad pa ci zhe na /
NK131(do)005:192: rjes thob tu gshis kyi bzhugs tshul go yul tsam
NK131(do)005:193: la nges pa rnyed pa'i phyir te shes byas sgro
NK131(do)005:194: 'dogs gcod pa na 'jig rten pa'i brda dang bstun
NK131(do)005:195: nas yul yul can gyi cha nas lta ba zhes
NK131(do)005:196: tha snyad du byas pa nyid rgyu'i theg par grags
NK131(do)005:197: che de lta na'ang gsang sngags su de'i rigs pas
NK131(do)005:198: rgyas 'gebs kyis bden pa gnyis la dpyad ra byas
NK131(do)005:199: pas 'bras bu'i theg pa rgyu'i rang sa nas 'phags
NK131(do)005:200: par ma nus / gang gi phyir na kun rdzob
NK131(do)005:201: lha'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom pa la tshig tsam mthun
NK131(do)005:202: yang don du ma mthun te dag pa gsum gyi
NK131(do)005:203: grub mthas kun rdzob gdod nas dag pa'i lha'i dkyil
NK131(do)005:204: 'khor du shes pa ma h+aa yo ga'i rang sa'i
NK131(do)005:205: grub mtha' yin kyang 'khrul snang gi 'dzin zhen ma
NK131(do)005:206: thongs pas gdod nas dag pa'i chos la yid mi
NK131(do)005:207: ches bzhin du lha bsgoms kyang rnal ma'i don la
NK131(do)005:208: ji tsam 'byor brtag par bya ba ste /
NK131(do)005:209: rdo rje 'chang chen po'i gsang ba lam gyi rim
NK131(do)005:210: pa'i grub mtha' thun mong ma yin pa ji bzhin
NK131(do)005:211: slong bar dka'/ des na lta ba zhes pa'i tshig
NK131(do)005:212: tsam la 'khrul nas gsang sngags kyi nyams myong gi
NK131(do)005:213: ye shes kyang dpyad pas gtan la 'bebs dgos par
NK131(do)005:214: smra ba ni cung zad mi legs te mdo sngags
NK131(do)005:215: gnyis spros bral gyi dgongs pa len tshul mi mtshungs
NK131(do)005:216: pa'i khyad kyis rdo rje theg par thabs rmad du
NK131(do)005:217: byung ba du ma'i rten cing 'brel 'byung las ye
NK131(do)005:218: shes tshegs med par car phog tu rtogs pa las
NK131(do)005:219: dpyad pas gtan la 'bebs dgos par nam yang ma
NK131(do)005:220: bstan pa'i phyir rgyu 'bras theg chen gnyis po rang
NK131(do)005:221: sa'i shes rab rlabs po ches zab mo'i gnas 'jal
NK131(do)005:222: ba la ma rmongs par bya ba ni chos spyi'i
NK131(do)005:223: don 'grel khyad par du 'phags pa yin no //
NK131(do)005:224: 'o na sngags kyi bden pa gnyis 'jal lugs khyad par yod dam zhe na /
NK131(do)005:225: yod de 'bras bu'i theg pa las /
NK131(do)005:226: don dam bden pa sems nyid gdod nas rang bzhin
NK131(do)005:227: gyis rnam par dag pa dbyings dang ye shes zung
NK131(do)005:228: du 'jug pa de nyid don dam pa'i de bzhin
NK131(do)005:229: gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK131(do)005:230: phrin las dang dbyer med pa'i lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK131(do)005:231: chos nyid cig tu 'jog pa yin la /
NK131(do)005:232: de 'dra de bka' 'khor lo tha ma nas bstan
NK131(do)005:233: pa'i bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po zab gsal gnyis
NK131(do)005:234: med du gsungs pa de las nam yang gnyis su
NK131(do)005:235: ma yin la / lus can kun gyi rgyud la gdod nas bzhugs shing /
NK131(do)005:236: bzhugs tshul yang glo bur gyi dri mas g.yogs pa
NK131(do)005:237: snying po'i tshul du bzhugs pas gzhi dus dang 'bras
NK131(do)005:238: dus gnyis bum nang gi mar me ltar dri mas
NK131(do)005:239: bsgribs ma bsgribs tsam las ngo bo la khyad med
NK131(do)005:240: de snying po'i mdo sde rnams su dpe du mas
NK131(do)005:241: don gcig po de nyid bstan pa dang /
NK131(do)005:242: rgyal tshab chen po byams pas mdo'i dgongs pa 'grel pa na /
NK131(do)005:243: sangs rgyas pad ngan sbrang rtsi sbrang ma la /
NK131(do)005:244: sogs dpe dgu dang sbyar bas snying po'i bzhugs tshul
NK131(do)005:245: rgyas par bkral ba bzhin rgyu'i theg pa'i mthar thug
NK131(do)005:246: gi nges don gang yin pa dang sngags kyi theg
NK131(do)005:247: pa gcig tu 'babs pa'i phyir mtshan nyid kyi theg
NK131(do)005:248: pa'i nges don mthar thug pa gang la gnas pa
NK131(do)005:249: sngags kyi dgongs pas 'byed pa nyid rgyu 'bras theg
NK131(do)005:250: chen gnyis kyi zab gsang rmad du byung ba la
NK131(do)005:251: lta ba'i blo mig rdo rje 'chang chen po'i lam
NK131(do)005:252: gyis phye ba las 'byung ba ste gzhan du /
NK131(do)005:253: rnal 'byor pa yang blo khyad kyis //
NK131(do)005:254: 'og mar gong ma dag gis gnod //
NK131(do)005:255: ces gsungs pa ltar lam 'og ma'i khyad par gong
NK131(do)005:256: mas 'byed pa las rang sa'i shes rab kyis rnam
NK131(do)005:257: par 'byed mi nus te ral gris rang gi so
NK131(do)005:258: mi gcod pa'i rigs pa dang mtshungs so //
NK131(do)005:259: de bas na tshul de dag ni zab pa dang
NK131(do)005:260: rgya che ba'i rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa bsam
NK131(do)005:261: gyis mi khyab pas bstan don /
NK131(do)005:262: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis bkral ba sogs nges
NK131(do)005:263: don la rton pa'i rgyal sras 'phags pa bgrangs kyis
NK131(do)005:264: mi lang pas rnam pa thams cad nas thams cad
NK131(do)005:265: du gsal zhing rgyas par mdzad grub pa'i phyir 'dir
NK131(do)005:266: smos ma dgos shing spros pas chog ste /
NK131(do)005:267: rtsa rgyud brtag pa gnyis pa kho nar yang //
NK131(do)005:268: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK131(do)005:269: 'on kyang glo bur dri mas bsgribs //
NK131(do)005:270: de bsal na ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK131(do)005:273: snga ma phyi ma khyad med kyang //
NK131(do)005:274: sgrib pa kun gyi dri med pa //
NK131(do)005:275: de bzhin nyid ni sangs rgyas 'dod //
NK131(do)005:276: ces pa la sogs kyis rnam pa kun tu bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)005:277: de la brten nas sngags kyi theg pa pas gzhi gang du /
NK131(do)005:279: dri mas gang sbyong ba'i tshul ji lta ba bzhin du shes pa dang /
NK131(do)005:280: bcing grol gyi gzhir gyur pa'i bdag dam pa de nyid shes par 'gyur ba dang /
NK131(do)005:281: de nyid mu stegs byed kyis kun tu brtags pa'i
NK131(do)005:282: bdag dang mi 'dra zhing rdo rje'i bdag tu gsungs
NK131(do)005:283: pa dang / gzhi dang 'bras bu'i rgyud dag gis nges par 'byed pa dang /
NK131(do)005:284: rim pa gnyis sgrub pa'i gzhi gang yin pa dang /
NK131(do)005:285: theg pa gnyis kar thun mong du grags pa'i gnas
NK131(do)005:286: yongs su gyur pa zhes bya ba de nyid ngo
NK131(do)005:287: shes pa sogs kyi rnam gzhag zab mo thams cad
NK131(do)005:289: 'o na bka' phyi ma dang gsang sngags su snying
NK131(do)005:290: po'i bzhugs tshul gsungs pa las bka' bar par snying
NK131(do)005:291: po'i ngos 'dzin ma gsungs sam zhe na /
NK131(do)005:292: snying po tsam ni gsungs mod /
NK131(do)005:293: ngos 'dzin tshul mi mtshungs te 'di pas rang bzhin
NK131(do)005:294: sher phyin dang snying po don gcig cing de'i spros
NK131(do)005:295: pa gcod tshul med dgag kho na las gzhan mi
NK131(do)005:296: 'chad pa'i rgyu mtshan lus can rnams kyi blo lhan
NK131(do)005:298: mu stegs byed rnams kyi grub mtha' ngan pas btags
NK131(do)005:299: pa'i bdag lta las bzlog pa'i skabs gtso bor ston
NK131(do)005:302: rgyal ba kun gyis stong nyid ni //
NK131(do)005:303: lta kun nges par 'byin par gsungs //
NK131(do)005:305: dngos po'i 'dzin pa bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK131(do)005:306: stong nyid bdud rtsi ston par mdzad //
NK131(do)005:307: ces gsungs pas kyang gsal lo //
NK131(do)005:308: de bzhin du ngo bo nyid med pa'i gzhung rnams
NK131(do)005:309: su snying po'i ngos 'dzin rgyas par mi bzhugs kyang
NK131(do)005:310: shes bya thams cad stong pa nyid du ro gcig
NK131(do)005:311: pa la bsams nas sems can thams cad snying po
NK131(do)005:312: can du bshad pa yin la /
NK131(do)005:313: des na snying po'i ngos 'dzin dang /
NK131(do)005:314: de nyid rgyu'i rgyud sogs su 'jog pa'i rnam bzhag
NK131(do)005:315: gong du smras pa rnams byed pa de srid du
NK131(do)005:316: bka' 'khor lo phyi ma gzhir bzhag nas rnam gzhag
NK131(do)005:317: byed pa nyid legs shing mtha' chod pa yin no
NK131(do)005:318: // de lta min par spyir thos bsam gyis gzhal
NK131(do)005:319: ba'i chos spyi'i stong nyid dang bye brag rang stong
NK131(do)005:320: ba bzhed pa'i dri bcas kyi sems bden pas stong
NK131(do)005:322: med dgag gi stong nyid la chos kyi dbyings su
NK131(do)005:323: 'dod pa de tsam zhig sngags kyi theg pa'i sbyang
NK131(do)005:324: gzhi rgyu'i rgyud sogs su 'jog par byed na /
NK131(do)005:325: de dag la zab pa dang rgya che ba'i mtshan
NK131(do)005:326: nyid can gyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba dang zung
NK131(do)005:327: du 'jug pa dang mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen
NK131(do)005:328: po'i khyad par sogs mi mnga' ba'i phyir thun mong
NK131(do)005:329: gi min pa'i skabs 'dir don dam bden pa rtogs
NK131(do)005:330: bya'i yul du 'jog mi nus te /
NK131(do)005:332: rdul phra rab tshogs pa'i bdag nyid kyi chos rnam
NK131(do)005:333: par dpyad pa'i stong pa chad pa'i stong pa nyid
NK131(do)005:335: nang gi bde ba rang rig par bya ba'i chos la rjes su chags pa /
NK131(do)005:338: gzhan gyis brjod min lhan cig skyes //
NK131(do)005:339: gang du yang ni rnyed min te //
NK131(do)005:340: bla ma'i dus thabs man ngag dang //
NK131(do)005:341: bdag gi bsod nams las shes bya //
NK131(do)005:342: zhes gsungs pa'i rkang pa dang pos gang rtogs par
NK131(do)005:343: bya ba brjod med lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes
NK131(do)005:344: zab gsal gnyis med bstan nas rkang pa gzhan gsum
NK131(do)005:345: pos de nyid rtogs byed bla ma ye shes can
NK131(do)005:346: gyis slob ma snod ldan gyi rgyud dang 'tshams par
NK131(do)005:347: man ngag gi rten 'byung ma 'phyug pa sogs las
NK131(do)005:348: rtogs par nus pa las gzhan gang gis kyang mi
NK131(do)005:350: ci ste lta ba spros bral las lhag pa med
NK131(do)005:351: kyang rtogs byed thabs kyi khyad par tsam mo zhe
NK131(do)005:352: na / lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la spros bral gyi mtshan nyid tshang yang /
NK131(do)005:353: spros bral tsam la de'i yon tan ma tshang zhing med de /
NK131(do)005:354: rigs shes kyis dgag bya bkag zin pa'i shul du
NK131(do)005:355: stong nyid rjes mthun pa 'grub kyang des lhan skyes
NK131(do)005:356: kyi ye shes mtshon par mi nus pa sogs kyi
NK131(do)005:357: phyir dang / gal te rigs shes kyis dpyad pa'i
NK131(do)005:358: stong pa las gzhan du lhan skyes kyi ye shes
NK131(do)005:360: gang du yang ni rnyed min te //
NK131(do)005:361: zhes pa'i tshig gi dgos pa stor bar 'gyur la /
NK131(do)005:362: mu stegs byed la sogs kyis kyang snying po'i de kho na nyid rtogs par thal te /
NK131(do)005:363: rigs shes ltar snang gis kyang de rtogs par nus pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)005:364: rkang pa gsum pa dang bzhi pa'i don yang gzhan te bla ma'i man ngag dang /
NK131(do)005:365: sngags kyi thabs lam sogs la ltos mi dgos par grub bo //
NK131(do)005:366: gzhan yang gsang sngags kyi don ston pa'i bla ma
NK131(do)005:367: de nyid sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam pa'am lhag par
NK131(do)005:368: gsungs pa lhan skyes kyi ye shes ston par mdzad
NK131(do)005:370: ye shes de nyid klog pa pa'i dpyad don tsam dang gcig par bsams na /
NK131(do)005:371: de ston pa'i bla ma yang klog pa'i slob dpon
NK131(do)005:372: dang mnyam par thal ba'i blo skyon 'di rang bzhin
NK131(do)005:374: bod 'dir phyis su de lag len du'ang bkal te
NK131(do)005:375: gsang sngags nyan pa la rtog ge slob pa'i 'du
NK131(do)005:377: des mos gus dang dag snang ri bong gi rwa ltar dkon pa'i dngos por gyur /
NK131(do)005:378: rgyu des byin rlabs dang dngos grub kyang rgyang ring du gyur tam snyam mo //
NK131(do)005:379: des na kye rdo rje'i dka' 'grel bla ma dpyal
NK131(do)005:380: lo ts+aa ba'i bshad sgros rtog ges ma bslad pa
NK131(do)005:382: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes de ji ltar rtogs she na /
NK131(do)005:383: gzhan gyis brjod min zhes pa gzhan la pa ra ma zer /
NK131(do)005:384: de ltar na mchog gi don du'ang 'gyur bas mchog rdo rje 'chang chen po yin la /
NK131(do)005:385: des kyang brjod du btub pa min no //
NK131(do)005:386: de gang zhe na lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes so //
NK131(do)005:387: de bsam pa'am btsal bas rnyed dam zhe na /
NK131(do)005:388: mi rnyed de sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpas kyang
NK131(do)005:389: yid kyi yul gang du yang ni mi rnyed de
NK131(do)005:390: bsam pa'i yul las 'das pas so //
NK131(do)005:391: 'o na de rtogs pa'i thabs yod dam zhe na yod de /
NK131(do)005:392: gzhan gyis brjod du mi btub pa de gzhan stobs kyis kyang rtogs te /
NK131(do)005:393: bla ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i dus kyi thabs ni /
NK131(do)005:394: gsum pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bsten pas rtogs so //
NK131(do)005:395: bla ma'i dus tshig zer na dbang bzhi pa'i dus su tshig gis ngo sprad pa'i sgo nas rtogs /
NK131(do)005:396: dus tshigs zer na rlung ma zin zer yang zin par yong ste des gsum pa'i dus su rtogs /
NK131(do)005:397: rlung ma zin pa gcig gis bzhi pa'i dus su rtogs so //
NK131(do)005:398: bla ma dam pa'i zhal nas 'di la gu ru
NK131(do)005:399: pa ra kra ma zhes bya ba bla ma'i man
NK131(do)005:400: ngag gi rim pa 'ba' zhig gis rtogs par 'gyur
NK131(do)005:401: gsungs kyang / gang du yang mi rnyed pa de rang stobs kyis kyang rtogs par gsungs te /
NK131(do)005:402: bdag gis bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pa las kyang rtogs par shes par bya'o //
NK131(do)005:403: zhes pa la sogs kyis ni de kho na nyid kyi ye shes gsal por bstan pa dang /
NK131(do)005:404: de bas na brjod med lhan cig skyes pa zab
NK131(do)005:405: cing phra ba'i bdag nyid can gyi ye shes 'di
NK131(do)005:406: nyid thos bsam gyi shes rab ltar snang gi yid
NK131(do)005:407: dpyod dang / tha snyad kyi dpe dang tshig gis
NK131(do)005:408: gtan la ji bzhin mi phebs par bdag cag gi
NK131(do)005:409: ston pas mdo rgyud thams cad du yang bka' stsal
NK131(do)005:410: dpyod dang / te / phyag chen thig le'i rgyud las kyang //
NK131(do)005:411: nyon cig lha mo phyag rgya che //
NK131(do)005:412: phyag rgya chen po gsang ba che //
NK131(do)005:413: brjod med mi zad ma skyes pa //
NK131(do)005:414: thams cad gzugs can gzugs dang bral //
NK131(do)005:415: gzugs med gzugs kyi dam pa mchog /
NK131(do)005:416: sbom phra la sogs dang bral ba //
NK131(do)005:417: gzhal du med pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK131(do)005:420: kha dog yi ge yon tan dpe bral ba //
NK131(do)005:421: smra ru mi btub de ni bdag gis gyi nar mtshon //
NK131(do)005:422: gzhon nu ma yi bde ba snying la zhugs pa bzhin //
NK131(do)005:423: dbang phyug dam pa de ni su la bstan nus sam //
NK131(do)005:425: thun mong gi theg pa chen po dkon mchog sprin las kyang /
NK131(do)005:426: chos 'di ni yi ge thams cad las yang dag par 'das pa /
NK131(do)005:427: smra ba thams cad las yang dag par 'das pa /
NK131(do)005:428: tshig gi spyod yul thams cad las yang dag par 'das pa /
NK131(do)005:429: ngag gi lam thams cad las 'das pa /
NK131(do)005:430: spros pa thams cad bral ba /
NK131(do)005:431: blang ba dang dor ba thams cad dang bral ba /
NK131(do)005:432: phyi ba dang btsum pa thams cad dang bral ba /
NK131(do)005:433: rtog ge thams cad bral ba /
NK131(do)005:434: brtag par bya ba ma yin pa /
NK131(do)005:435: rtog ge'i spyod yul ma yin pa /
NK131(do)005:436: rtog ge'i spyod yul las yang dag par 'das pa /
NK131(do)005:437: zhes pa la sogs rgyu 'bras theg chen gnyis kyi
NK131(do)005:438: ye shes ngo bo'i bzhugs tshul sgra ji bzhin pa
NK131(do)005:439: drang thad du ston pa'i skabs don gcig pa nyid
NK131(do)005:442: shes rab snying por 'dus byas kyi chos thams cad
NK131(do)005:443: ngo bo nyid med cing spang thob dang bral bar
NK131(do)005:444: gsungs pa'o // de la dgongs nas chos kyi rjes bstan bcos 'dir /
NK131(do)005:445: dbu ma las lhag lta yod na //
NK131(do)005:446: lta de spros pa can du 'gyur //
NK131(do)005:447: zhes gsungs pa 'di'i dgongs pa ji bzhin blang tshe /
NK131(do)005:448: sngags kyi lta ba bde stong lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK131(do)005:449: ye shes zab gsal gnyis med de nyid ngo bo'i
NK131(do)005:450: cha nas spros pa'i mtha' gang du'ang ma ltung ba
NK131(do)005:451: la dgongs nas lta ba de'i mtshan nyid spros pa
NK131(do)005:453: de ltar yin pas spros bral gyi cha nas dbu ma'i spros bral las lhag pa med /
NK131(do)005:454: de med pas spros bral gyi ngos nas dbu ma
NK131(do)005:455: dang gsang sngags khyad par med par 'chad pa'i don
NK131(do)005:458: spros bral yin na khyad par med //
NK131(do)005:460: spros bral de yang spyir yod med sogs gang du'ang khas blang med pa'i don tsam las /
NK131(do)005:461: bod 'ga' zhig gi zhe 'dod ltar med dgag gi stong nyid kho nar bzhed pa min zhing /
NK131(do)005:462: spros bral de la rnam pa'i bde ba chen po
NK131(do)005:463: dang so so rang rig gi rig pas nyams su
NK131(do)005:464: myong byar gyur pa sngags kyi lta ba'i khyad chos
NK131(do)005:465: su bzhed pa yin te 'chad par 'gyur bas shes
NK131(do)005:466: so // des na lta ba zhes pa spros bral
NK131(do)005:467: gyi ming tsam la mthun na'ang spros bral de'i dgongs
NK131(do)005:468: pa'i len tshul rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gnyis khyad
NK131(do)005:469: par che ba la rtog ge'i rigs pa ltar snang
NK131(do)005:470: gi thos bsam gyis dpyad pa de mdo sngags gnyis
NK131(do)005:471: kar dgos par bsam pa phal cher zhig la shar
NK131(do)005:473: dbang dus kyi ye shes de thos bsam gyi lta ba dang mnyam mam lhag /
NK131(do)005:475: thos bsam gyis dpyad pas kyang lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK131(do)005:476: ye shes rtogs par thal te de nyid de'i lta
NK131(do)005:478: 'dod na sngags kyi thabs la ltos mi dgos par grub pas de don med par 'gyur ba dang /
NK131(do)005:480: dbang dus su lhag pa'i ye shes rtogs par byar
NK131(do)005:481: yod bzhin du sngon du thos bsam gyis dpyad pa
NK131(do)005:483: des nyams myong gi lta bar mi btub pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)005:484: ci ste ngo bo la khyad par med kyang rtogs byed thabs kyi bye brag tsam mo //
NK131(do)005:485: zhe na rtogs bya'i lta ba la khyad par ma
NK131(do)005:486: grub pa bzhin du thabs de dag gang yang rung
NK131(do)005:487: bas rtogs par nus pa'i phyir gnyis ka bstan pa
NK131(do)005:489: yang myur bul gyis dbye ba tsam du 'dod na
NK131(do)005:490: yang lam de gnyis kas bgrod bya sangs rgyas kyi
NK131(do)005:491: ye shes su gcig kyang ye shes de la nye
NK131(do)005:492: ba dang ring ba'i khyad shin tu che zhing zung
NK131(do)005:493: 'jug gi rgyu mthun lam du byed pa yod med
NK131(do)005:494: sogs rdo rje 'chang gi lam thun mong ma yin
NK131(do)005:495: pa'i khyad par gyi chos ji snyed cig mchis pa
NK131(do)005:496: de snyed kyis mchog dman yod de /
NK131(do)005:497: bstan bcos 'di nyid mdzad pa pos kyang /
NK131(do)005:498: thos bsam gyis gzhal ba'i stong nyid la rgyu dus kyi lta ba dug can du gsungs nas /
NK131(do)005:499: des nyams myong gi go ma chod par dbang gi
NK131(do)005:500: ye shes la nyams su myong bya'i lta ba sangs
NK131(do)005:501: rgyas kyi sa'i ye shes dang ngo bo gcig par
NK131(do)005:503: des na gnas skabs su mdo sngags so so'i rang
NK131(do)005:504: sa'i shes rab mi zab pa dang zab pa dang
NK131(do)005:505: ches zab pa'i khyad par dang /
NK131(do)005:506: de rtogs byed thabs kyi khyad par sogs kyi ldog
NK131(do)005:507: pa ma 'dres pa la blo gros kyi mig dkyus
NK131(do)005:508: ring po thob par bya dgos te /
NK131(do)005:509: de ltar ma yin na phyogs re'i blo gros kyi
NK131(do)005:510: lam du rgyu 'bras theg pa gnyis po 'gal ba
NK131(do)005:511: ltar snang gi gzugs brnyan las ldog par dka' zhing
NK131(do)005:512: dgongs pa gcig tu gzigs pa'i mkhas pa chen po
NK131(do)005:513: rnams kyis gnas skabs kyi grub matha'i zhal bzhes tsam
NK131(do)005:514: mdzad pa la nges don du bzung na byis pa'i
NK131(do)005:515: blo gros mgo 'khor nas 'bras bu'i theg pa'i khyad
NK131(do)005:516: par gyis chos rnams mtshan nyid rang sa nas 'phags
NK131(do)005:518: rdo rje 'chang gi gsang ba thun mong ma yin
NK131(do)005:519: pa de dang de rnams kyi dgongs pa chud mi
NK131(do)005:520: gson par thal mo sbyar nas gsol ba 'debs so
NK131(do)005:521: // ci nas dpyad pa sngon du ma song bar
NK131(do)005:522: rtags par mi 'gyur na dbang dus su'ang thos bsam
NK131(do)005:523: gyi dpyang pa la brten nas lhan skyes kyi ye
NK131(do)005:524: shes skye dgos par thal ba'i skyon 'di yang spang
NK131(do)005:525: // dka' zhing / de lta bu de ni rdo
NK131(do)005:526: rje 'chang gis nam yang ma gsungs mi gsung gsung
NK131(do)005:528: 'on kyang dbang dus lta ba ngo sprod pa'i tshe
NK131(do)005:529: dpyad pa mi dgos mod kyi lta don de nyid
NK131(do)005:530: rjes su sgom pa la sbyar ba'i tshe dpyad pa
NK131(do)005:531: dang bcas pas bsgom par bya dgos so zhe na
NK131(do)005:532: / ngo 'phrod pa'i lta ba de skabs der lhan
NK131(do)005:533: skyes kyi ye shes mtshon bya mtshon byed kyi sgo
NK131(do)005:534: nas ngo bo rjen par nyams su myong ba la
NK131(do)005:535: de der ngo sprod pa las ma 'das pa'i phyir
NK131(do)005:536: mngon sum nyams myong du gtan la phebs zin pa'i
NK131(do)005:537: rjes su dpyad pa don med cing rgyu 'bras go
NK131(do)005:538: log gi skyon gnas pa dang /
NK131(do)005:539: sgom pa la sbyor ba'i tshe na'ang rtogs shing ngo
NK131(do)005:540: 'phrod pa'i don de nyid la mnyam par bzhag pas
NK131(do)005:543: gal te gsang sngags bsgom 'dod na //
NK131(do)005:544: nor ba med pa'i dbang bzhi longs //
NK131(do)005:545: 'khrul pa med pa'i rim gnyis sgoms //
NK131(do)005:546: de las byung ba'i ye shes ni //
NK131(do)005:547: phyag rgya chen po goms par bya //
NK131(do)005:548: zhes gsungs pas sngags kyi ye shes de la thos
NK131(do)005:549: bsam gyi rgyu tshogs med ka med kyi yan lag
NK131(do)005:550: tu bzhed pa ma yin no //
NK131(do)005:551: lta ba rtogs zin pa'i rjes su dpyad pa mi
NK131(do)005:552: dgos pa ni dbu ma'i man ngag gi dgongs pa'ang
NK131(do)005:553: yin te shing gnyis drag tu drug pa las me
NK131(do)005:554: 'ba' bas de dag tshig par gyur pa na me
NK131(do)005:555: nyid kyang rang zhir 'gyur ba bzhin du so sor
NK131(do)005:556: rtog pa'i shes rab kyang dmigs pa med pa'i ngang
NK131(do)005:557: du zhi bar gyur pa na shes rab kyi pha
NK131(do)005:558: rol tu phyin pa nyid rtogs par gsungs pa bzhin
NK131(do)005:559: no // des na dpyad pas gtan la 'bebs par
NK131(do)005:560: bstan pa thams cad rgyu'i theg pa'i skabs kho na
NK131(do)005:561: dang de yang las dang po pas thog mar thos
NK131(do)005:562: bsam la brten nas don 'ol spyi'i tshul du rtogs
NK131(do)005:563: par 'gyur ba la dgongs par shes dgos /
NK131(do)005:564: thos bsam gyis chos spyi'i lta ba rjes dpag gi
NK131(do)005:565: tshul du rtogs pa zhig sngags la zhugs na dbang
NK131(do)005:566: dus sogs kyi thabs la brten nas mngon sum nyams
NK131(do)005:567: myong gi ting nge 'dzin skyes pa'i tshe sngar gyi
NK131(do)005:568: go yul sa bon gyi tshul du gnas pa de
NK131(do)005:569: nyid nyams myong gi ye shes su na 'phar ba
NK131(do)005:571: gzhan du thos bsam sngon du ma song ba yang
NK131(do)005:572: sngags la zhugs pa'i tshe dbang gsum pa lta bu'i
NK131(do)005:573: thabs kyis lta ba ma 'khrul pa'i ye shes mngon
NK131(do)005:574: sum du rtogs pas grol bar 'gyur ba rdo rje
NK131(do)005:575: 'chang gi myur lam 'di'i khyad par gyi chos su
NK131(do)005:576: rtsod pa med de in+d+ra b+h+au ti sogs 'phags yul
NK131(do)005:578: bod 'dir yang rje btsun mi la dang gling ras
NK131(do)005:579: rjes 'brangs dang bcas pa'i rnam thar gyis kyang shes
NK131(do)005:581: bstan bcos 'di nyid kyi bzhed pa'i snying po yang der nges te /
NK131(do)005:582: des na grub thob thams cad kyang //
NK131(do)005:583: phyogs re'i thabs kyis grol ba min //
NK131(do)005:584: dbang dang rim gnyis las byung ba'i //
NK131(do)005:585: ye shes skyes pas grol ba yin //
NK131(do)005:586: zhes gsal bar bshad pa dang /
NK131(do)005:587: gzhan yang gzhan gyis brjod min sogs lung gong du drangs zin pa dang /
NK131(do)005:588: gang gis mi shes kye rdo rje //
NK131(do)005:589: de yis ngal ba don med yin //
NK131(do)005:590: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK131(do)005:592: nyin bzhin bram ze gsod pa dang //
NK131(do)005:593: mtshams med lnga ni byed pa dang //
NK131(do)005:594: chom rkun las kyis longs spyod pa'ang //
NK131(do)005:596: sdig pas gos par mi 'gyur zhing //
NK131(do)005:597: srid pa'i skyon las shin tu ring //
NK131(do)005:598: zhes pa la sogs rgya cher gsungs pa rnams kyang
NK131(do)005:599: sngon du bstan pa la zhugs shing spyod pa de
NK131(do)005:600: dang des 'tsho bzhin pa rnams kyang lam 'di dang
NK131(do)005:601: 'phrad pa tsam gyis grol bar 'gyur ba'i don 'di
NK131(do)005:602: nyid la dgongs nas gsungs par snang ba'i phyir ro
NK131(do)005:603: // rgyu mtshan de rnams kyi phyir bstan bcos 'dir /
NK131(do)005:604: des na thos pa'i lta ba ni /
NK131(do)005:605: dbu ma yan chad thams cad mthun //
NK131(do)005:606: de phyir lta ba'i lung sbyor kun //
NK131(do)005:607: pha rol phyin bzhin thams cad mdzad //
NK131(do)005:608: de rtogs byed pa'i thabs la ni //
NK131(do)005:609: theg pa'i rim pa yod pa min //
NK131(do)005:610: zhes gsungs pas thos pas gtan la dbab pa'i lta ba yin phyin chad go ba las ma 'das /
NK131(do)005:612: gsang sngags khyad par med pas gtan la 'bebs tshul
NK131(do)005:613: pha rol phyin pa bzhin du shing rta'i ring lugs
NK131(do)005:614: chen po rnams las 'byung ba bzhin bya ba las
NK131(do)005:615: 'os med cing de lta bu rtogs par byed pa
NK131(do)005:616: la theg pa'i rim pa yod pa ma yin no
NK131(do)005:617: // zhes ston pa las gsang sngags kyi nyams su
NK131(do)005:618: myong ba'i ye shes de nyid go yul gyi lta
NK131(do)005:619: ba dang khyad par med par ston pa'i tshig ma
NK131(do)005:620: // yin te / des na thos pa'i lta ba ni /
NK131(do)005:621: zhes nges gzung mdzad pa dngos bstan dang /
NK131(do)005:622: de lta min na go ba'i lta ba des grol dgos pa la /
NK131(do)005:623: lta ba dang ni bskyed rim dang //
NK131(do)005:624: gtum mo dang ni byin rlabs sogs //
NK131(do)005:625: de dag rkyang pas grol ba min //
NK131(do)005:626: zhes go yul gyi lta ba de tsam gyis mi grol bar bshad nas /
NK131(do)005:627: dbang bskur ba yi byin rlabs dang //
NK131(do)005:628: rim gnyis bsgoms pa'i rten 'brel gyis //
NK131(do)005:629: ye shes rtogs nas grol ba yis //
NK131(do)005:630: zhes pas gsang sngags kyi ye shes nyams myong kho
NK131(do)005:631: na la brten nas grol bar gsungs pa la bsnyon
NK131(do)005:633: gal te thos bsam mam rgyu dus kyi lta ba
NK131(do)005:634: las lhag pa gsang sngags su med pa gzhir bzhag
NK131(do)005:635: pa'i tshe na de lta bu des nyams su myong
NK131(do)005:636: ba'i lta ba'i go chod dgos pa la des go
NK131(do)005:637: mi chod par gsung ngag rin po che 'chad pa'i
NK131(do)005:638: skabs su de la rgyu dus kyi lta ba dug
NK131(do)005:639: can du ming btags nas lta ba dang grub mtha'
NK131(do)005:640: gnyis kyi zlas dbye ba'i lta ba de nyams myong
NK131(do)005:641: ting nge 'dzin gyi lta ba la bzhag /
NK131(do)005:642: de gang du nyams su myong zhe na lam dus
NK131(do)005:643: su myong ste dbang gi ye shes nyid las gzhan
NK131(do)005:644: du mi bzhed pas ting nge 'dzin gyi lta ba
NK131(do)005:645: der na 'phos dang po'i tshe grub mtha' la brtags
NK131(do)005:646: su shar te lta ba 'khor 'das dbyer med de
NK131(do)005:647: tsam na mngon sum du rtogs so //
NK131(do)005:648: zhes 'chad bar snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK131(do)005:649: de dang mtshungs par rje klu sgrub kyis /
NK131(do)005:650: bstan bcos 'di yi dgongs pa 'chad pa na //
NK131(do)005:651: lta ba de yi yan lag yin //
NK131(do)005:653: gzhan gyi rtsod pa spong pa'i skabs /
NK131(do)005:655: kho bo cag lta ba de la rtogs pa tsam la lta bar bzhag pa'i lta ba gcig dang /
NK131(do)005:656: nyams myong ting nge 'dzin la lta bar bzhag pa'i
NK131(do)005:657: lta ba gnyis su phye nas snga ma ni rgyu
NK131(do)005:658: dus kyi lta ba dug can zhes bshad pa de
NK131(do)005:660: lta ba de yi yan lag yin /
NK131(do)005:661: zhes pa de thos bsam gyi lta ba de la zer ba lags /
NK131(do)005:662: lta ba dang grub mtha' gnyis kyi lta ba de
NK131(do)005:663: ni nyams myong ting nge 'dzin gyi lta ba de
NK131(do)005:664: la 'jog cing / de skabs kyi lta ba de
NK131(do)005:665: 'jig rten pa'i lam man chad na yod kyang spyir
NK131(do)005:667: 'di'i grub mtha' bzhi po gang rung la nyams myong
NK131(do)005:668: ting nge 'dzin gyi lta ba'i mchog mtshon bya don
NK131(do)005:669: gyi phyag chen yin pas khyab pa khas blangs pa'i
NK131(do)005:670: phyir ro // de ltar bdag gis rang bzo ma yin te /
NK131(do)005:672: sngon bla mas rgyu dus na bstan pa'i lta ba 'khor 'das dbyer med de tsam na rtogs /
NK131(do)005:673: zhes 'khor 'das dbyer med lta khrid kyi skabs su
NK131(do)005:674: bstan pa'i lta ba de lam dus su nyams su
NK131(do)005:675: myong ste / ting nge 'dzin gyi lta ba der
NK131(do)005:676: na 'pho sa dang po'i tshe grub mtha' la rtags
NK131(do)005:677: su shar te lta ba 'khor 'das dbyer med mngon
NK131(do)005:678: myong ste / sum du rtogs / grub mtha' dang
NK131(do)005:679: po 'khor 'das dbyer med ces grags pa der 'pho
NK131(do)005:680: myong ste / sum du rtogs / bar / rje btsun rin po che grags pa'i zhabs kyis /
NK131(do)005:681: dbang gi ye shes lam gyi lta ba ni //
NK131(do)005:682: nyams myong sangs rgyas sa dang ngo bo gcig /
NK131(do)005:683: rtogs pa'i khyad par zla ba'i dpe yis bstan //
NK131(do)005:684: zhes gsungs pa'ang drangs nas gsal bar bshad 'dug pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)005:685: de bzhin du pan chen rin po che sh+aakya mchog ldan gyis kyang /
NK131(do)005:686: thos bsam dus kyi stong pa nyid //
NK131(do)005:687: dngos po'i gnas lugs ma yin te //
NK131(do)005:688: de yi yul can rtog pa las //
NK131(do)005:689: ma 'das phyir na de goms pa //
NK131(do)005:690: dug can nyid du bshad phyir ro //
NK131(do)005:691: zhes nyams su myong bya'i lta ba rang byung gi
NK131(do)005:692: ye shes bzo bcos bral ba nyid du bshad do
NK131(do)005:693: // des na thos bsam gyis dpyad pa'i lta ba
NK131(do)005:694: de go yul tsam las gnas lugs ji lta ba
NK131(do)005:695: // min pa dang / dbang dus su nyams su
NK131(do)005:696: myong ba'i lta ba de gnas lugs ji ltar ba'i
NK131(do)005:697: rang byung gi ye shes su rje btsun sa skya
NK131(do)005:698: pa rjes 'brangs dang bcas pa'i bzhed pa ma nor
NK131(do)005:699: ba nyid du nges pa gzu po'i blos shes par
NK131(do)005:700: bya dgos pa ni de dag gi thun mong dang
NK131(do)005:701: thun mong ma yin pa'i gsungs rab rnams la 'dris
NK131(do)005:702: par mdzod cig dang rtogs par 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)005:703: der ma zad dbu mar rang lugs su'ang /
NK131(do)005:704: rags pa phyi'i dbu ma dang phra ba nang gi
NK131(do)005:705: dbu ma gnyis su mdzad pa'i snga ma pha rol
NK131(do)005:706: dang rtsod pa dang gzhung chen po 'dzugs pa dang
NK131(do)005:707: / rtsom pa'i dus su bstan zhing /
NK131(do)005:708: phyi ma nang gi rnal 'byor nyams su len byar
NK131(do)005:709: shing rta chen po pa dag gi dgongs par gnas
NK131(do)005:710: pa slob dpon b+ha bya sogs kyis gsal bar bshad
NK131(do)005:712: rgyud des gnas skabs su stong tshul gnyis kyang shin tu tha dad de /
NK131(do)005:714: stong nyid bag chags goms pa yis //
NK131(do)005:715: dngos po'i zhen pa spong bar 'gyur //
NK131(do)005:716: zhes dngos zhen las ldog pa'i phyir chos thams cad
NK131(do)005:717: rang ngo nas bden pa bkag pa'i stong nyid bstan
NK131(do)005:718: yang / dngos zhen ldog par gyur nas stong 'dzin
NK131(do)005:719: gyi blo dang ma bral na stong pa nyid du
NK131(do)005:720: 'dzin pa'i gdon chen por 'gyur ba'i phyir rtag par
NK131(do)005:721: lta ba las kyang tha chad par bstan te /
NK131(do)005:723: 'od srungs bdag tu 'dzin pa ni ri rab tsam yang bla yi /
NK131(do)005:724: bdag med par lta ba ni de lta ma yin /
NK131(do)005:727: gang dag stong pa nyid lta ba //
NK131(do)005:728: de dag bsgrub tu med par gsungs //
NK131(do)005:729: zhes pa la sogs pas gsal la /
NK131(do)005:731: ci yang med ces goms pa las //
NK131(do)005:732: de yang phyi nas spong bar 'gyur //
NK131(do)005:733: zhes ci yang med pa'i stong pa de spangs nas
NK131(do)005:734: slar de las zab pa'i stong pa nyid la goms
NK131(do)005:735: su yod par gsungs pa'i phyir dang khyad par du
NK131(do)005:736: gsang sngags kyi thog pa bar khas len bzhin du
NK131(do)005:737: phung po rnams dpyad kyi rang stong kho na las
NK131(do)005:738: ches zab pa'i stong pa nyid kyi tshul gzhan mi
NK131(do)005:740: bcom ldan 'das spyan ras gzigs kyis /
NK131(do)005:741: gang zhig phung po la sogs sgrib pa rab bcom yul ni pra phab brgyad lta bu //
NK131(do)005:742: kun mkhyen bde ster de nyid gcig pu rdo rje 'dzin pa'i phyag rgya chen mo ste //
NK131(do)005:743: zhes pas gzhi 'bras ngo bo dbyer med kyi phyag rgya chen mo dang /
NK131(do)005:744: rnam pa thams cad kyi mchog dang ldan pa'i stong nyid dang /
NK131(do)005:745: yum sher phyin ji lta ba sogs kyi mtshan nyid rnams med par 'gyur te /
NK131(do)005:746: rang stong tsam gyis de rnams kyi go mi chod pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)005:747: gzhan yang rang stong dang don dam pa'i bden pa rnams grangs su 'dod na /
NK131(do)005:748: sgrib pa gnyis kyang rang stong yin pa'i phyir don dam bden par 'gyur la /
NK131(do)005:750: de gnyen po gang gis kyang spang du mi rung bar 'gyur zhing /
NK131(do)005:751: 'phags pa'i ye shes dam pa'i rang rig gi spyod
NK131(do)005:752: yul yang ya na par 'gyur ba'i phyir dang khyad
NK131(do)005:753: par rdo rje 'chang chen pos rgyud sde rin po
NK131(do)005:754: che rnams su gsang ba zhes pa dang /
NK131(do)005:755: gsang chen zhes pa la sogs pas stong nyid mthar
NK131(do)005:756: thug gi rnam grangs gsungs pa gang yin pa rang
NK131(do)005:757: stong la dgongs pa ni ma yin te gal te
NK131(do)005:758: de yin na / phyi nang thun mong gi rtog
NK131(do)005:759: ge dang rigs pa ltar snang gis kyang rtogs par
NK131(do)005:760: 'gyur bas gsang ba chen por bstan pa'i dgos pa
NK131(do)005:761: de yin na / nyams shing / de ltar na
NK131(do)005:762: nyer len gyi phung po lnga yang rang stong yin
NK131(do)005:763: pa'i phyir mtha' thug nges don gyi gsang ba yin
NK131(do)005:764: de yin na / nyams shing / par 'gyur la / 'dod na /
NK131(do)005:765: de rnams sher phyin yin par ha cang thal bar 'gyur te /
NK131(do)005:766: phyag na rdo rje'i zhal snga nas /
NK131(do)005:767: gsang ba zhes pa drang ba'i don gyis las kyi phyag rgya'i b+ha gar brjod do //
NK131(do)005:768: nges pa'i don ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stong pa nyid do //
NK131(do)005:769: zhes gzhi 'bras dbyer med kyi sher phyin stong nyid du gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)005:770: zhes pa sogs kun mkhyen chen po dol po pas rgyas par bshad do //
NK131(do)005:772: kha cig dbu ma'i lta ba ni //
NK131(do)005:773: kun rdzob ji ltar snang bzhin yin //
NK131(do)005:774: don dam mtha' bzhi spros dang bral //
NK131(do)005:775: bya ba'i rgyud kyi kun rdzob ni //
NK131(do)005:776: rigs gsum rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NK131(do)005:777: don dam dbu ma dang mtshungs zer //
NK131(do)005:778: spyod pa'i rgyud kyi kun rdzob dang //
NK131(do)005:779: rnal 'byor rgyud kyi kun rdzob ni //
NK131(do)005:780: rigs lnga'i rgyal bar snang ba yin //
NK131(do)005:781: rnal 'byor chen po'i kun rdzob ni //
NK131(do)005:782: dam pa rigs brgya yin zhes zer //
NK131(do)005:783: lta sgom rnam dbye ma phyed cing //
NK131(do)005:784: thabs dang shes rab ma phyed pas //
NK131(do)005:787: de la mkhas pa chen po 'ga' zhig gis lta sgom rnam dbye ma phyed ces pa /
NK131(do)005:788: lta ba'i yul gnas lugs kyi don dang /
NK131(do)005:789: yul can de rtogs pa'i shes rab la bshad nas /
NK131(do)005:790: snang ba lha'i dkyil 'khor du lta ba bsgom pa yin zhing lta ba min pa'i shes byed du /
NK131(do)005:791: sgom pa ni gnas lugs dang mthun pa'i nges pa med de /
NK131(do)005:792: byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems sgom pa bzhin no //
NK131(do)005:793: zhes 'chad par mdzad pa de ni thun mong gi theg pa ltar gsungs par mngon la /
NK131(do)005:794: thun mong ma yin pa'i theg pa 'dir don gcig na yang ma rmongs shing /
NK131(do)005:795: zhes pas bsgrub bya sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang gcig
NK131(do)005:796: kyang ma rmongs zhes pa lta ba'i khyad par la
NK131(do)005:798: dpal 'khor lo sdom pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rgyud las /
NK131(do)005:799: nyan thos la sogs theg chung la //
NK131(do)005:800: man ngag yod pa ma yin te //
NK131(do)005:801: lta ba spyod pa sems bzung dang //
NK131(do)005:802: rgyu dang lam dang 'bras bu sa //
NK131(do)005:803: dus dang rnal 'byor longs spyod dang //
NK131(do)005:804: bdag gzhan don dang dgongs pa dang //
NK131(do)005:805: ngal dub mtha' spangs tshegs chung dang //
NK131(do)005:806: tshogs bsags pa yi khyad par dang //
NK131(do)005:807: khyad par rnam pa bco lnga yis //
NK131(do)005:809: zhes pa 'dis lta ba'i khyad par bshad cing /
NK131(do)005:813: sogs bdun gyis gsang sngags 'phags par bshad par yang
NK131(do)005:814: lta ba'i khyad par nges par bshad pa yin no
NK131(do)005:815: // 'o na lta ba de khyad par cis 'phags pa yin zhe na /
NK131(do)005:816: mdo tsam sngar yang smras zin la /
NK131(do)005:817: chos thams cad spros pa nye bar zhi ba khas
NK131(do)005:818: len thams cad dang bral ba ni mdo lugs la'ang
NK131(do)005:819: yod mod / da lta'i rig pa 'di spu ma
NK131(do)005:820: barjesa par sangs rgyas su 'grub par 'dod pa ni
NK131(do)005:821: pha rol tu phyin pa la ga la yod de
NK131(do)005:822: yod mod / / gnas de ni gsang sngags bla
NK131(do)005:823: na med pa'i rang sa'i shes rab rmad du byung
NK131(do)005:824: yod mod / / ba yin la / de bzhin
NK131(do)005:825: du kun rdzob bden pa'i mtshan nyid kyang rnam par
NK131(do)005:826: dag pa dang ma dag pa'i lta ba'i yul du
NK131(do)005:827: byed tshul la khyad par shin tu che ste /
NK131(do)005:828: rgyu'i theg par kun rdzob kyi chos thams cad 'khrul
NK131(do)005:829: snang ma dag pa'i log shes yin pa gzhir bzhag
NK131(do)005:830: nas de nyid bden med du gtan la dbab pa
NK131(do)005:831: tsam las gdod nas rnam par dag pa'i sku dang
NK131(do)005:832: zhing khams kyi dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin du lta
NK131(do)005:834: rgyu des don gcig na yang ma rmongs zhes pa
NK131(do)005:835: 'dis phar phyin la rmongs pa'i sgrib pa phyogs gcig
NK131(do)005:838: phyi snang ba'i bden zhen bzlog pa la sgyu mar
NK131(do)005:839: bsgom pa la sogs pas 'byung ba'i rigs la rmongs
NK131(do)005:840: / nang phung po lhar ma shes pas gnas pa don la rmongs /
NK131(do)005:841: gsang ba rtogs tshogs dang nyon mongs pa ye shes
NK131(do)005:842: su ma shes pas lam gyi rnam pa la rmongs
NK131(do)005:843: / thams cad dag mnyam bden pa dbyer med du
NK131(do)005:844: ma shes pas rtogs pa'i lta ba la rmongs pa
NK131(do)005:845: nyid kyis kun rdzob spang bya dang don dam blang
NK131(do)005:846: byar byas pas gnyis med dag mnyam chen po'i don
NK131(do)005:848: des kun 'byung spang gnyen gyi sgo nas sdug bsngal
NK131(do)005:849: spong ba tsam las med cing sbyin sogs bsod nams
NK131(do)005:850: kyi tshogs gsog pa'ang thabs la mi mkhas pas grangs
NK131(do)005:851: med gsum gyi mtha' la 'bras bu thob par bstan
NK131(do)005:852: / gzugs sku gnyis kyi rgyu mthun yang sgra ji bzhin pa ma bstan te /
NK131(do)005:853: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim du //
NK131(do)005:854: gnyis med ma rtogs thams cad la //
NK131(do)005:855: bden bzhi'i dngos po yod lta zhing //
NK131(do)005:856: spong dang mi spong byed gyur na //
NK131(do)005:857: 'di ni nyan thos sa pa yin //
NK131(do)005:858: las dang nyon mongs thams cad la //
NK131(do)005:859: mnyam pa'i don du mi shes shing //
NK131(do)005:861: 'di ni rang sangs rgyas kyi sa //
NK131(do)005:862: mnyam pa'i don nyid mi shes shing //
NK131(do)005:863: kun rdzob don dam gnyis 'byed la //
NK131(do)005:864: chos dang gang zag bdag med na //
NK131(do)005:865: 'di ni byang chub sa pa yis //
NK131(do)005:867: gang dag 'bras bu'i rnam pa 'dra ba zhig lta
NK131(do)005:868: ba'i yul du byas nas de nyid sgom pas lam
NK131(do)005:869: du byed pa mdo sngags gnyis kyi dgongs pa yin
NK131(do)005:870: na / gsang sngags su gzugs sku gnyis kyi 'bras
NK131(do)005:871: bu sgrub pa'i phyir kun rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor du
NK131(do)005:872: gsungs shing de nyid lam du byed pa'i lta ba
NK131(do)005:873: dang sgom pas khyad par du 'phags pa ste rgyu'i
NK131(do)005:874: theg par gzugs sku gnyis dang de'i rgyu mthun ji
NK131(do)005:875: bzhin pa ma bstan pa ni /
NK131(do)005:876: ji skad du rje btsun rin po che grags pa rgyal mtshan gyis /
NK131(do)005:877: gang dang gang du 'bras bu ma bstan pa de na de'i lam med pa nyid yin te /
NK131(do)005:878: dper na nyan thos kyi sde snod du sku gsum
NK131(do)005:879: dang ye shes bzhi la sogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK131(do)005:880: chos ma grags pa der yang de thob par byed
NK131(do)005:881: pa'i lam ma bstan par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)005:882: yang pha rol tu phyin pa'i theg par ye shes
NK131(do)005:883: lnga rigs lngar bstan pa la sogs pa ma grags
NK131(do)005:884: pa der yang de lta bu'i lam med par shes
NK131(do)005:885: par bya'o // de bzhin du kye'i rdo rje ma
NK131(do)005:886: bstan pa der yang kye rdo rje'i lam med par
NK131(do)005:887: par bya'o // shes par bya'o // zhes kyee rdor gyi 'grel par gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK131(do)005:888: gzhan yang sngags lam la 'jug pa'i gang zag de
NK131(do)005:889: ni chos thams cad dag mnyam chen por lta ba'i
NK131(do)005:890: shes rab la gdeng du gyur pa nyid kyis skal
NK131(do)005:891: ba dang ldan zhing dngos grub kyi snod du rung
NK131(do)005:893: bden gnyis bzang ngan blang dor gyi spu ris 'byed
NK131(do)005:894: pa'i blo rtog ni dngos grub kyi gegs su rdo
NK131(do)005:895: rje 'chang gis rgyud sde rnams su yang yang bka'
NK131(do)005:896: stsal zhing / khyad par phung po la brnyas pas
NK131(do)005:897: rtsa ba'i ltung ba brgyad pa dang dgu pa rang
NK131(do)005:898: bzhin lhun grub tu 'byung ba'i don la'ang dran pa
NK131(do)005:900: 'o na kun rdzob ltar lta ba'i tshul ji lta bu zhe na /
NK131(do)005:901: tshul de la mkhas pa kye rdo rje'i dka' 'grel
NK131(do)005:902: bla ma dpyal lo ts+aa ba'i gsung las 'di ltar
NK131(do)005:903: 'byung ste / de la spros pa gcod lugs gnyis yod de ming dang don gnyis so //
NK131(do)005:904: ming gi spros pa gcod pa ni /
NK131(do)005:905: chu lta bu gcig la bod pas chu zer /
NK131(do)005:907: rgya gar pa rnams kyi sa u da ka zer /
NK131(do)005:908: de bzhin du dngos po gcig la tha mal pas gzugs kyi phung po zer /
NK131(do)005:909: rnal 'byor bas rdo rje ma zer ba yin no //
NK131(do)005:910: don gyi spros pa gcod lugs ni /
NK131(do)005:911: dngos po gcig mi'i 'gro ba la chu ru snang /
NK131(do)005:912: yi dwags la rnag khrag tu snang /
NK131(do)005:913: lha la bdud rtsir snang ba bzhin du dngos po
NK131(do)005:914: gcig tha mal pa la gzugs kyi phung por snang
NK131(do)005:915: / rnal 'byor pa la rdo rje mar snang ba la bya gsungs so //
NK131(do)005:916: zhes bshad pa la 'dis snang ba dag ma dag
NK131(do)005:917: gi cha la bden par yod pa zhig sbyang gzhir
NK131(do)005:918: byas nas / de'i ma dag pa'i cha de nyid sbyang bya'i dri ma dang /
NK131(do)005:919: dag pa'i cha de nyid sbyangs 'bras su 'thad pa
NK131(do)005:920: gsang sngags kyi grub mtha' 'cha' tshul thun mong dang
NK131(do)005:921: ma 'dres pa de nyid shes par bya ba'i gnad
NK131(do)005:923: gal te rgyu'i theg par sbyang gzhi ma bstan pa'i
NK131(do)005:924: phyir rgyu 'bras nang 'gal bar 'gyur ro zhe na
NK131(do)005:925: / skyon med de bka' dang po gnyis su sbyang
NK131(do)005:926: gzhi ma bstan pa ni chos kyi 'khor lo de
NK131(do)005:927: dag gis chos dang gang zag gi bdag skye med
NK131(do)005:928: du gtan la phab nas kun 'byung gzhi med du
NK131(do)005:929: spong ba yin pas na de spang pa'i gzhi bstan
NK131(do)005:930: na gang zag gi bdag spong bar mi 'gyur te
NK131(do)005:931: / / kun 'byung dang 'jig tshogs la lta ba
NK131(do)005:932: thams cad kyi rtsa ba bdag tu 'dzin pa las
NK131(do)005:933: byung ba'i phyir de'i rtsa ba skye med du ma
NK131(do)005:934: chod na kun 'byung spang bar mi nus par dgongs
NK131(do)005:936: len pa'i rnam par shes pa zab cing phra //
NK131(do)005:937: sa bon thams cad chu bo bzhin du 'bab //
NK131(do)005:938: bdag tu rtog par 'gyur na mi rung bas //
NK131(do)005:939: ngas 'di byis pa rnams la ma bstan to //
NK131(do)005:941: des na gsang sngags su kun 'byung spang byar mi
NK131(do)005:942: byed cing lam du khyer ba'i tshul gyi thabs la
NK131(do)005:943: mkhas pas spong ba dper na mes tshig pa me
NK131(do)005:944: nyid la bsro bas sel ba dang /
NK131(do)005:945: rna bar chu zhugs pa chu nyid kyis 'don pa
NK131(do)005:946: bzhin du 'dod chags kyi nyon mongs pa 'dod chags
NK131(do)005:947: nyid kyi lam gyis spong bar byed pa lta bus
NK131(do)005:948: mtshon sbyang bya dang rnam pa mtshungs pa'i sbyong byed
NK131(do)005:949: khyad par ba bsgoms pas sbyang gzhi ma dag pa'i
NK131(do)005:950: gnas skabs su gang zag gi bdag dang /
NK131(do)005:951: dag pa'i gnas skabs su gnyis su med pa'i ye
NK131(do)005:952: shes dam pa'i bdag dang rdo rje'i bdag ces tha
NK131(do)005:953: snyad du byas pa de dag gi ma dag gi
NK131(do)005:954: gnas skabs su yod nges pa zhig gzhir bzhag nas
NK131(do)005:955: de'i steng gi ma dag pa'i cha de rnams sbyang
NK131(do)005:957: gzhi la yod pa'i yon tan rnams mngon du gyur
NK131(do)005:958: pa'i tshe sbyangs 'bras su tha snyad gdags pa ste
NK131(do)005:959: mdor na nyon mongs pa spong tshul mi 'dra ba'i
NK131(do)005:960: dbang gis mdo sngags so so'i shes rab kyi khyad
NK131(do)005:961: par la go ba lhongs pa gal che zhing /
NK131(do)005:962: phar phyin rang lugs su'ang bka' bar pas chos thams
NK131(do)005:963: cad skye med du gtan la phab nas lta ba'i
NK131(do)005:964: gzhi kun bzlog pa yin yang tha mas sbyangs gzhi
NK131(do)005:965: bde gshegs snying po sgra ji bzhin par bstan pas
NK131(do)005:966: sngags kyi dgongs pa dang 'byor zhing rgyu 'bras kyi
NK131(do)005:967: theg chen gnyis kar grags pa'i gnas yongs su gyur
NK131(do)005:968: pa dang / ngo bo la dag par bya rgyu'i chos med pa dang /
NK131(do)005:969: thob bya'i 'bras bu'ang sngar med gsar du sgrub pa
NK131(do)005:970: med pa'i tshul rnams bstan pa ni mdo sngags gnyis
NK131(do)005:971: car dgongs pa gcig pa ste /
NK131(do)005:973: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK131(do)005:974: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK131(do)005:977: ji ltar mar me bum nang gnas //
NK131(do)005:978: cung zhig snang bar mi 'gyur ba //
NK131(do)005:979: de bzhin nyon mongs bung nang gnas //
NK131(do)005:980: chos kyi dbyings kyang mi mthong ngo //
NK131(do)005:983: rang rig bdag nyid dag pa nyid //
NK131(do)005:984: dag pa gzhan gyis rnam grol min //
NK131(do)005:985: zhes pa'i 'grel bar chos phung po khams skye mched
NK131(do)005:986: la sogs pa rnams dngos po la grub par gnas
NK131(do)005:987: pa zhig lus ngag yid gsum gyi 'bad rtsol gyis
NK131(do)005:988: dag par byas pa ma yin /
NK131(do)005:989: 'o na lus ngag yid gsum gyi 'bad rtsol la
NK131(do)005:990: brten nas lam nyams su blangs pas chos nyid kyi
NK131(do)005:991: don mthong ba de 'bad rtsol gyis dag par byas
NK131(do)005:992: pa ma yin nam zhe na /
NK131(do)005:993: 'bad rtsol gyis chos nyid kyi don mthong ba'i tshe
NK131(do)005:994: na yang gzhi la sngar mi gnas pa zhig mthong
NK131(do)005:995: ba ma yin / gzhi la gnas pa'i don gsal bar byas pa tsam yin gyi des na /
NK131(do)005:996: gzhi la sngar ma dag pa zhig dag par byas pa ma yin te /
NK131(do)005:997: dper na bum pa'i nang na gnas pa'i mar me
NK131(do)005:998: de bum pa bcag pa la brten nas gsal bar
NK131(do)005:999: byas pa yin gyi sngar mi gnas pa zhig gsal
NK131(do)005:1000: bar byas pa ma yin pa bzhin no //
NK131(do)005:1001: dag bya gang dag pa ni nyon mongs zhes pa sgrib pa de dag go //
NK131(do)005:1002: de yang glo bur ba ma yin gyi rang bzhin nam ngo bo nyid kyis rnam par dag go //
NK131(do)005:1003: gang gis dag na rang rig tsas pa chos thams
NK131(do)005:1004: cad rang gi sems rang rig pa bde ba rtog
NK131(do)005:1005: pa med par gnas pa de nyid kyis dag pa
NK131(do)005:1006: nyid yin gyi / zhes pa la sogs pa rdo
NK131(do)005:1007: rje'i tshig 'grel rtog ges ma spags par bkral ba
NK131(do)005:1008: nyid yin gyi / bzhin no // des na sems
NK131(do)005:1009: kyi chos nyid gdod nas rnam par dag pa'i dbyings
NK131(do)005:1010: ye shes zung du 'jug pa'i rtsal chos can kun
NK131(do)005:1011: rdzob ltar snang ba'i phung po khams dang skye mched
NK131(do)005:1012: thams cad kyang rnam par dag pa'i sku dang zhing
NK131(do)005:1013: khams gzhal yas khang gi bkod pa tha mi dad
NK131(do)005:1014: kyi rol pa mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lor lhun
NK131(do)005:1015: grub tu zhugs par shes pa ste /
NK131(do)005:1016: bzhugs tshul yang dag pa gsum gyi mtshan nyid du
NK131(do)005:1017: gdod nas rang bzhin gyis grub pa nyid der shes
NK131(do)005:1018: par bya ba tsam las gsar du sems rtog glo
NK131(do)005:1019: bur bas bzo 'chos pa ma yin te /
NK131(do)005:1021: phyi 'byung la lnga yum lngar rnam par dag /
NK131(do)005:1022: nang phung po lnga yab lngar rnam par dag /
NK131(do)005:1023: rtog tshogs byang chub sems dpa'i bdag nyid ye shes
NK131(do)005:1024: lngar rnam par dag pas 'khor 'das dbyer med dag
NK131(do)005:1025: mnyam chen por gtan la 'bebs pa sngags rang sa'i
NK131(do)005:1026: shes rab bla na med par grub par nges te
NK131(do)005:1030: 'khor ba spangs pa'i pha rol na //
NK131(do)005:1031: mya ngan 'das pa yong ma yin //
NK131(do)005:1032: zhes pa'i don 'grel par 'di nyid 'khor ba zhes
NK131(do)005:1033: pa chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis lhan skyes yin
NK131(do)005:1034: te ngo ma shes na 'khor ba zhes bya /
NK131(do)005:1035: lhan skyes 'di nyid ngo shes na mya ngan las 'das pa nyid kyang yin no //
NK131(do)005:1036: 'o na 'khor ba spang ngam zhe na /
NK131(do)005:1037: de spangs nas gzhan du mya ngan las 'das pa rtogs pa'am rnyed par mi 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)005:1038: zhes gsungs pa 'dis grub mtha' slong ste /
NK131(do)005:1039: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dpal gsang ba 'dus pa las /
NK131(do)005:1040: mdor na phung po lnga rnams ni //
NK131(do)005:1041: sangs rgyas lngar ni rab tu bsgrags //
NK131(do)005:1042: rdo rje skye mched nyid dag kyang //
NK131(do)005:1043: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK131(do)005:1045: sa ni spyan ma zhes bya yin //
NK131(do)005:1046: chu yi khams ni m+aa ma k+ai //
NK131(do)005:1047: dkar dang sgrol ma zhes bya ba //
NK131(do)005:1048: me dang rlung dang rab tu grags //
NK131(do)005:1049: mkha' dbyings rdo rje'i dam tshig ni //
NK131(do)005:1050: rdo rje 'dzin pa de nyid yin //
NK131(do)005:1053: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK131(do)005:1054: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK131(do)005:1055: skye mched khams rnams mang po kun //
NK131(do)005:1056: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK131(do)005:1057: srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas zhing //
NK131(do)005:1058: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan pa'i chos //
NK131(do)005:1059: sangs rgyas nyid kyis mi brnyes so //
NK131(do)005:1061: 'jam dpal gyi rang gi lta ba'i 'dod pa rje
NK131(do)005:1062: n+aa ro pan chen dang slob dpon a tsa la
NK131(do)005:1064: gzugs kyi tshogs pa mtha' yas pa //
NK131(do)005:1065: bdag gi sprul pa'i sku mchog go //
NK131(do)005:1066: sgra yi phung po mtha' yas pa //
NK131(do)005:1067: bdag gi longs spyod rdzogs sku mchog /
NK131(do)005:1068: chos kyi phung po mtha' yas pa //
NK131(do)005:1069: bdag gi chos skur rab tu bsgrags //
NK131(do)005:1070: bde ba'i phung po mtha' yas pa //
NK131(do)005:1071: bdag gi bde sku 'gyur med mchog /
NK131(do)005:1072: bsdus pa phung po de bzhin du //
NK131(do)005:1073: yang dag bsags par yongs su bsgrags //
NK131(do)005:1074: zhes pa la sogs rnam pa du mas gsungs pa'i
NK131(do)005:1075: dag mnyam chen po'am gzhi 'bras dbyer med kyi grub
NK131(do)005:1076: pa'i mtha' chen por gdod nas gnas pa la lta
NK131(do)005:1077: ba'i shes rab 'di nyid yod pas kun 'byung lam
NK131(do)005:1078: du khyer nas sdug bsngal bde bar sgyur ba la
NK131(do)005:1079: ma rmongs pas snang ba lha'i dkyil 'khor /
NK131(do)005:1080: grags pa sngags kyi sgra gdangs /
NK131(do)005:1082: sgul skyod lha'i phyag rgya sogs spyod yul thams cad
NK131(do)005:1083: gu yangs phya ma gdal chen por bsod nams kyi
NK131(do)005:1084: tshogs su song bas skal chen grangs med gsum tshe
NK131(do)005:1085: gcig sogs su bzlums nas rdo rje 'chang gi sar
NK131(do)005:1086: 'gro bar phyir thabs mang ba dang dka' ba med
NK131(do)005:1087: pas myur lam du grub pa yin la /
NK131(do)005:1088: de'i phyir slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i zhal snga nas /
NK131(do)005:1089: thabs kyi theg pa chen por ni //
NK131(do)005:1090: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dang //
NK131(do)005:1091: kun rdzob tu yang dbyer med pas //
NK131(do)005:1092: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK131(do)005:1094: gal te 'o na rgyud sde 'og ma gsum du
NK131(do)005:1095: snang ba lha'i dkyil 'khor du ma gsungs pa ci
NK131(do)005:1096: zhe na skabs de'i gdul bya lta ba mnyam pa
NK131(do)005:1097: chen po'i don la blo ma 'byor bas spyod pa
NK131(do)005:1098: blang dor med par 'jug ma nus /
NK131(do)005:1099: de ma nus pas sgom pa bdag dang lha gnyis
NK131(do)005:1100: su dpon g.yog sogs su blta ba'i mtha' la zhen
NK131(do)005:1102: blo stobs kyi rim pas theg pa dang rgyud sde
NK131(do)005:1103: gong 'og byung zhing der dag mnyam chen pa'i grub
NK131(do)005:1104: mtha' dngos su ma gsungs kyang lha sgom pa'i rim
NK131(do)005:1105: pa bstan pas / don gyis der 'du ba ni
NK131(do)005:1106: nyan thos kyi mdo dang theg par stong pa nyid
NK131(do)005:1107: sgra ji bzhin par bstan na blor mi shong ba
NK131(do)005:1108: la dgongs nas bdag med pa'i sgras gsungs nas stong
NK131(do)005:1109: pa nyid kyi tshul rgyas par theg chen du gtan
NK131(do)005:1110: la phab pa dang mtshungs pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1111: spyir theg dman gyi sbas don thams cad theg chen du rgyas shing gsal /
NK131(do)005:1112: rgyu'i theg pa'i sbas don thams cad gsang sngags su rgyas shing gsal /
NK131(do)005:1113: sngags kyi mdo dang rgyas pa thams cad rnal 'byor
NK131(do)005:1114: bla med nyid du gsal zhing rgyas par bstan par
NK131(do)005:1115: shes dgos te / sangs rgyas gsang bas /
NK131(do)005:1116: bla med theg pa'i nang nas ni //
NK131(do)005:1117: don dam du ni dbyer med de //
NK131(do)005:1118: kun rdzob tu ni thams cad la //
NK131(do)005:1119: dag dang ma dag gnyis kar 'dzin //
NK131(do)005:1121: de lta bu'i rnal 'byor bla med rang sa'i grub
NK131(do)005:1122: matha'i 'cha' tshul 'di rje btsun sa skya pa bzhed
NK131(do)005:1124: thun mong gi bstan bcos 'chad pa'i skabs 'ga' zhig
NK131(do)005:1125: ma gtogs rgyud kyi dgongs pa sgra ji bzhin du
NK131(do)005:1126: bkral ba na de kho na ltar bzhed par nges
NK131(do)005:1127: pa'i tshad ma gnyis shig yod de /
NK131(do)005:1128: dang po rje btsun 'khrul pa'i dri ma spangs pa
NK131(do)005:1129: grags pa rgyal mtshan gyis rtsa ltung rnam bshad du
NK131(do)005:1130: / phung po sangs rgyas lnga bdag nyid //
NK131(do)005:1131: de la smod pa brgyad pa yin //
NK131(do)005:1133: bdag gi lus 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rang bzhin te /
NK131(do)005:1134: phung po lnga ni sangs rgyas lnga'i rang bzhin /
NK131(do)005:1135: khams bzhi ni lha mo bzhi'i rang bzhin /
NK131(do)005:1136: nang gi skye mched ni byang chub sems dpa'i ngo bo /
NK131(do)005:1137: phyi'i skye mched rnams ni lha mo'i rang bzhin te /
NK131(do)005:1138: de skad du gsang ba 'dus pa las /
NK131(do)005:1139: mdor na phung po lnga rnams ni //
NK131(do)005:1140: sangs rgyas lngar ni rab tu bshad //
NK131(do)005:1141: rdo rje skye mched nyid dag ni //
NK131(do)005:1142: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK131(do)005:1143: sa ni spyan zhes bya ba ste //
NK131(do)005:1144: chu khams de bzhin m+aa ma k+ai //
NK131(do)005:1145: drod dang rlung zhes bya ba ni //
NK131(do)005:1146: dkar dang sgrol ma zhes byar brjod //
NK131(do)005:1148: shes rab ma'i rgyud las kyang //
NK131(do)005:1149: gzugs phung rdo rje ma yin te //
NK131(do)005:1150: tshor ba la ni dkar mor brjod //
NK131(do)005:1153: rnam shes phung po'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK131(do)005:1154: bdag med rnal 'byor ma gnas so //
NK131(do)005:1155: zhes bya ba la sogs pa rgyas par gsungs so //
NK131(do)005:1156: zhes lung de dag drangs te /
NK131(do)005:1157: des na lus rang bzhin gyis sangs rgyas yin pa la sogs pas rgyas par bshad cing /
NK131(do)005:1159: rang bzhin dag pa'i chos rnams la //
NK131(do)005:1160: som nyi za ba dgu pa yin //
NK131(do)005:1162: chos thams cad ngo bo nyid kyis dag pa'i rang
NK131(do)005:1163: bzhin med pa de bzhin nyid kyis dag pa dang
NK131(do)005:1164: / phung po lnga rgyal ba lnga'i rang bzhin du
NK131(do)005:1165: dag pa lha so so'i dag pa ste rang bzhin
NK131(do)005:1166: gyis dag pa gnyis la yin nam ma yin snyam
NK131(do)005:1167: pa'i the tshom zos pa'ang rtsa ba'i ltung bar 'gyur
NK131(do)005:1168: / na / rang bzhin gyis ma dag par 'dzin
NK131(do)005:1169: pa lta smos kyang ci dgos zhes pa sogs kyis
NK131(do)005:1171: de dang mtshungs pa rgyu'i theg chen du'ang 'byung tshul /
NK131(do)005:1172: 'phags pa sdong po bkod pa las /
NK131(do)005:1173: gzugs dang tshor ba 'du shes dang //
NK131(do)005:1174: rnam par shes dang sems pa ni //
NK131(do)005:1175: grangs med de bzhin gshegs pa rnams //
NK131(do)005:1176: de dag thub pa chen por 'gyur //
NK131(do)005:1177: zhes pa la sogs drangs nas bshad do //
NK131(do)005:1178: gnyis pa chos kyi rje pan+di tas mdzad pa'i bdag
NK131(do)005:1179: med bstod pa'i 'brel pa las rgyud gsum rnam par
NK131(do)005:1181: de la thog mar rgyu'i rgyud ni //
NK131(do)005:1182: rang bzhin dri med ces pa ste //
NK131(do)005:1183: rang gi sems kyi chos nyid rang bzhin gyis rtog
NK131(do)005:1184: pa'i dri ma thams cad dang bral ba yin te
NK131(do)005:1186: sangs rgyas ma yin sems can ni //
NK131(do)005:1187: gcig kyang yod pa ma yin te //
NK131(do)005:1190: chu khams gser dang nam mkha' bzhin //
NK131(do)005:1191: dag pa bzhin du dag par gnas //
NK131(do)005:1193: de lta na 'bad pa med par grol bar 'gyur ro zhe na ma yin te /
NK131(do)005:1194: blo gros glo bur gyi dri mas bsgribs pa /
NK131(do)005:1195: zhes smos te sems kyi chos nyid rang bzhin gyis
NK131(do)005:1196: dag kyang sems kyi mtshan nyid la glo bur dri
NK131(do)005:1197: mas bsgribs pa zhes bya ba'i don to //
NK131(do)005:1198: de ltar na rang bzhin gyis dag pa la glo
NK131(do)005:1199: bur du dri mas gos na 'bad pa dgos pa
NK131(do)005:1200: med par 'gyur ro zhe na ma yin te /
NK131(do)005:1201: glo bur gyi sgras ni sbyang du rung ba la bya yi /
NK131(do)005:1202: sngar med pa las phyis dri ma 'byung ba lta bu ma yin te /
NK131(do)005:1203: bcom ldan 'das kyis mdo las kyang /
NK131(do)005:1204: gang dag sbyang du rung ba'i chos de ni glo bur pa'o //
NK131(do)005:1206: des na gang dag gser grub pa'i dus su g.ya' grub mod kyang /
NK131(do)005:1207: g.ya' sbyangs na dag par 'gyur bas na /
NK131(do)005:1208: de la glo bur pa zhes gdags so //
NK131(do)005:1209: dri mas bsgribs pa zhes pa ni /
NK131(do)005:1210: nyon mongs dang shes bya'i sgrib pas thar pa'i go skabs bkag pa'o //
NK131(do)005:1212: gsal bar mdzad pa zhes pa ni nyon mongs pa
NK131(do)005:1213: dang shes bya'i sgrib pa'i g.ya' sbyangs te sems kyi
NK131(do)005:1214: gser gsal bar byed pa ste /
NK131(do)005:1216: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK131(do)005:1217: 'on kyang glo bur dri mas bsgribs //
NK131(do)005:1218: de nyid bsal na sangs rgyas nyid //
NK131(do)005:1220: zhes gsal zhing rgyas par gsungs shing de'i khungs kyang
NK131(do)005:1221: byams chos dang rgyud sde gnyis la mdzad pa yin
NK131(do)005:1222: no // des na gzhi'i gnas lugs la dag par
NK131(do)005:1223: bya rgyu'i chos rdul tsam med kyang re zhig de
NK131(do)005:1224: ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems kyi 'khrul snang glo bur
NK131(do)005:1226: gnas lugs de dang rnam pa mthun pa'i lam sgom
NK131(do)005:1227: pa ni dri ma sbyong ba'i gnyer por song ste
NK131(do)005:1228: sbyang bya rim gyis dag pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1229: gzhi la bzhugs pa'i yon tan rnams mngon du gyur
NK131(do)005:1230: pa'i rim pa la 'bras bu thob par tha snyad
NK131(do)005:1231: btags shing de'i phyir bskyed rim gyi lha sku bsgom
NK131(do)005:1232: pa yang spangs rtogs kyi rim pas tshogs lam du
NK131(do)005:1233: mos spyod kyi lha sku sbyor lam du rlung sems
NK131(do)005:1234: kyi lha sku / mthong lam du 'od gsal gyi lha sku /
NK131(do)005:1235: sgom lam du slob pa'i zung 'jug gi lha sku /
NK131(do)005:1236: sangs rgyas kyi sar mi slob pa'i zung 'jug gi lha skur 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK131(do)005:1238: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK131(do)005:1239: ces pa sogs gong du drangs pa'i don la sgra ji bzhin pa 'dir 'byor ba yin zhing /
NK131(do)005:1240: de ltar ma yin par shes bya gzhi'i skabs su rgyu'i rgyud dang /
NK131(do)005:1241: lam gyi gnas skabs su sbyang byed /
NK131(do)005:1242: 'bras bu'i dus su bral 'bras kyi sku dang ye
NK131(do)005:1243: shes sogs ri bong gi rwa dang mo gsham gyi
NK131(do)005:1244: bu ltar shes bya la med par mtha' gcig tu
NK131(do)005:1245: bzhed na de dang de'i rnam bzhag dang dgos pa
NK131(do)005:1246: rnams stong bar 'gyur zhing bskyed rim sogs sgom pa'ang
NK131(do)005:1247: med pa la yod par sgro 'dogs su 'gyur ba
NK131(do)005:1248: sogs skyon mang po zhig nye bar 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)005:1249: gsum pa la gnyis kyi dang po gzhung gis ston tshul ni /
NK131(do)005:1250: des na gsang sngags gsar ma la //
NK131(do)005:1251: rnal 'byor chen po'i ltag na ni //
NK131(do)005:1252: de bas lhag pa'i rgyud sde med //
NK131(do)005:1253: sgom pa'i dmigs pa nyid kyang ni //
NK131(do)005:1254: rnal 'byor chen po'i gong na med //
NK131(do)005:1255: de las skyes pa'i ye shes ni //
NK131(do)005:1256: spros pa med cing brjod bral bas //
NK131(do)005:1257: theg pa'i rim par mi bzhed do //
NK131(do)005:1258: lugs 'di legs par shes gyur na //
NK131(do)005:1259: a ti yo ga'i lta ba yang //
NK131(do)005:1260: ye shes yin gyi theg pa min //
NK131(do)005:1261: brjod bral brjod byar byas pa ni //
NK131(do)005:1262: mkhas pa'i dgongs pa min zhes bya //
NK131(do)005:1264: tshul 'dis gsang sngags gsar ma pa rnams la ma
NK131(do)005:1265: ha yo ga las lhag pa'am de'i gong du rgyud
NK131(do)005:1266: sde gzhan med / de med pas sgom pa'i rim pa'ang de las lhag pa med /
NK131(do)005:1267: de las skyes pa'i ye shes ni spros pas dben
NK131(do)005:1268: zhing brjod pa dang bral ba'i phyir theg pa dang
NK131(do)005:1269: rgyud sde'i go rim du mi bzhed ces pa ste
NK131(do)005:1270: / snga 'gyur pa la nang pa bskyed rdzogs gsum
NK131(do)005:1271: zhes yongs su grags pa'i bskyed pa ma h+aa yo
NK131(do)005:1272: / ga dang / rdzogs pa a nu yo ga
NK131(do)005:1273: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga gsum brjod
NK131(do)005:1274: bya rjod byed kyi sgo nas rgyud sde dang theg
NK131(do)005:1275: pa'i go rim du bzhag par byar yod bzhin du
NK131(do)005:1277: 'dus pa sogs su dkyil 'khor rgyal mchog gi ting
NK131(do)005:1278: nge 'dzin sgom pa'i bye brag tsam la rnal 'byor
NK131(do)005:1281: rnal 'byor chen po bzhi'i rim pa mdzad pa gnyis
NK131(do)005:1282: ming tsam mthun pa la dgongs nas de dag don
NK131(do)005:1283: gcig tu 'dzin pa yod dogs pas mi gcig pa'i
NK131(do)005:1284: khyad par gong du gsang sngags rnying ma pa rnams
NK131(do)005:1285: ni rnal 'byor rnal 'byor chen po dang /
NK131(do)005:1286: rjes su rnal 'byor shin tu ni //
NK131(do)005:1287: rnal 'byor zhes bya rnam pa bzhi //
NK131(do)005:1288: theg pa'i rim pa yin zhes zer //
NK131(do)005:1290: gsang sngags phyi 'gyur pa rnams ni //
NK131(do)005:1294: rgyud sde'i rim par mi bzhed do //
NK131(do)005:1295: zhes gsungs te de'i don 'chad pa na 'di skad
NK131(do)005:1296: du rnal 'byor chen po gzhir byas la rnal 'byor
NK131(do)005:1297: gsum du 'byed pa 'di spyir gsang ba 'dus pa
NK131(do)005:1298: la sogs pa'i rgyud las 'byung bas rnal 'byor gyi
NK131(do)005:1299: rim par 'thad kyang theg pa dang rgyud sde'i rim
NK131(do)005:1301: rnal 'byor bzhi'i nang gi rnal 'byor chen po dang /
NK131(do)005:1302: rgyud sde bzhi'i rnal 'byor chen po don mi gcig pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)005:1303: go rim yang mi mthun te /
NK131(do)005:1304: rnal 'byor bzhi'i nang gi bzang shos rnal 'byor chen po yin pa la /
NK131(do)005:1305: khyed theg pa rim dgu 'dod pa dag gis shin
NK131(do)005:1306: tu rnal 'byor bzang bar khas blangs pa'i phyir zhes
NK131(do)005:1308: gnyis pa skyon de spong ba la /
NK131(do)005:1309: spyir theg pa dgu'i grangs la klan ka mi 'jug pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1310: bye brag a nu a ti gnyis theg pa dang rgyud sde'i rim par 'thad pa sgrub pa'o //
NK131(do)005:1312: chos kyi rjes theg pa gsum yongs su grags pa'i dbang du mdzad pa yin la /
NK131(do)005:1313: rnying ma rang lugs su theg rim dgu'i rnam gzhag mdzad pa la don gyis rtsod pa med de /
NK131(do)005:1314: bde bar gshegs pas gdul bya so so'i blo dang
NK131(do)005:1315: mtshams par theg pa'i rim pa ji snyed cig gi
NK131(do)005:1316: rnam gzhag mdzad nas re zhig de dang des 'dul
NK131(do)005:1317: ba'i gdul bya drang ba'i thabs su bstan yang mthar
NK131(do)005:1318: thug sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bgrod pa gcig pa'i
NK131(do)005:1319: theg pa mchog la bkri ba'i ngal stegs tsam du
NK131(do)005:1320: dgongs pa ste / lam stegs kyi theg pa de
NK131(do)005:1321: rnams kyis rang rang dang rjes mthun gyi 'bras bu
NK131(do)005:1323: da dung gong nas gong du bgrod bya'i lam dang
NK131(do)005:1324: 'bras bu yod pa'i phyir dam pa'i chos pad+ma dkar
NK131(do)005:1325: po las / drang srong rnams kyis theg pa gsum bstan pa //
NK131(do)005:1326: rnam 'dren rnams kyi thabs la mkhas pa ste //
NK131(do)005:1327: theg pa gcig ste gnyis su yod ma yin //
NK131(do)005:1328: bkri ba'i don du theg pa gsum bstan to //
NK131(do)005:1330: des na theg pa chen po ni gcig nyid de
NK131(do)005:1331: gang du gnyis sam gsum du gsungs pa ni gnas
NK131(do)005:1332: skabs su ngal gso ba'i don tsam las theg pa
NK131(do)005:1333: dngos ma yin par bstan pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1334: theg chen gcig po de la'ang rgyu dang 'bras bu'i
NK131(do)005:1335: theg pa gnyis su dbye ba'i skabs 'bras bu'i theg
NK131(do)005:1336: pa bla na med pa nyid ma rtogs na nyan
NK131(do)005:1337: rang byang sems kri yog gi theg pa so sos
NK131(do)005:1338: rang sa'i mi mthun phyogs 'khor ba dang mtha' gnyis
NK131(do)005:1339: las nges par 'byung ba'i 'bras bu re thob kyang
NK131(do)005:1340: / bla na med pa'i theg pa gcig gang yin
NK131(do)005:1341: pa der gdod 'jug dgos te thob bya'i mthar thug
NK131(do)005:1342: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang de nyid lam
NK131(do)005:1343: bden mthar thug theg pa mchog nyid las 'byung dgos
NK131(do)005:1344: pa yin na der ma zhugs pas 'bras bu'i mthar
NK131(do)005:1345: thug pa thob par mi nus phyir /
NK131(do)005:1347: theg pa gsum gyis nges 'byung la //
NK131(do)005:1348: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK131(do)005:1349: zhes pa la sogs lung mang ba'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)005:1350: de bas na nyan rang byang sems kyi theg pa gsum dang /
NK131(do)005:1351: phyi ma la nang gses kyi dbye bas rdo rje'i
NK131(do)005:1352: theg pa ste bzhir 'gyur yang byang chub sems dpa'i
NK131(do)005:1353: theg par don gyis gcig tu bgrangs pa yin la
NK131(do)005:1354: / de bzhin du theg pa lngar gsungs pa'ang yod de /
NK131(do)005:1356: lha yi theg dang tshangs pa'i theg /
NK131(do)005:1357: de bzhin du ni nyan thos dang //
NK131(do)005:1358: de bzhin gshegs dang rang rgyal gyi //
NK131(do)005:1359: theg pa tha dad ngas bshad do //
NK131(do)005:1362: theg pa sna tshogs thabs tshul gyis //
NK131(do)005:1363: 'gro ba'i don la rtog pa po //
NK131(do)005:1364: zhes pas sna tshogs kyi sgra ni mang po'i don dang /
NK131(do)005:1365: y+aa na'i sgra ni thob byed dam /
NK131(do)005:1366: bzhon pa dang khyogs kyi don du 'gyur bas gang
NK131(do)005:1367: don du gnyer ba'i 'bras bu de nyid thob pa'i
NK131(do)005:1368: thabs sam yan lag tu gyur pa zhig ste 'khor
NK131(do)005:1369: ba nas myang 'das kyi bar gyi lam bden thams
NK131(do)005:1370: cad la spyir btang theg pa gcig gi sgra sbyar
NK131(do)005:1371: yang rung la / bye brag ji snyed pa de
NK131(do)005:1372: snyed du theg pa'i sgra sbyar yang mi 'gal te
NK131(do)005:1373: phyi'i nam mkha' dang khyim so so'i nam mkha' bzhin
NK131(do)005:1374: yang rung la / no // des na lang gshegs las /
NK131(do)005:1375: ji srid sems ni 'jug pa'i bar //
NK131(do)005:1376: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK131(do)005:1377: ces gsungs pa'i don yang 'di nyid la 'jug go //
NK131(do)005:1378: gzhan du theg pa gsum kho nar nges gzung btub pa'ang ma yin te /
NK131(do)005:1379: 'phags pa rtogs chen phyag rgya las /
NK131(do)005:1380: theg pa ni gcig kho nar nges te gnyis dang gsum du ma mchis so //
NK131(do)005:1383: rab 'byor theg pa ni gcig kho na ste bla na med pa'i sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'o //
NK131(do)005:1384: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa'i phyir mtha' gcig
NK131(do)005:1385: tu zhe na theg pa gsum du smra ba la'ang
NK131(do)005:1387: gzhan yang lha'i bu rab rtsal sems kyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK131(do)005:1388: theg pa chen po'i theg pa 'di //
NK131(do)005:1389: sangs rgyas theg pa bsam mi khyab //
NK131(do)005:1390: sems can gyi ni go skabs 'byed //
NK131(do)005:1391: theg pa chen po bla na med //
NK131(do)005:1392: theg pa ji snyed yod pa kun //
NK131(do)005:1393: 'di ni de yi mchog tu dgongs //
NK131(do)005:1394: de'i phyir theg pa chen po las //
NK131(do)005:1395: theg pa thams cad rab tu dbye //
NK131(do)005:1396: zhes gsungs pas ji snyed kyi sgra ni mang po'i
NK131(do)005:1397: don te de'i phyir lam gyi chos thams cad la
NK131(do)005:1398: dgongs pa dang / theg pa de thams cad kyi
NK131(do)005:1399: dbye gzhi theg pa chen po gcig kho nar bstan
NK131(do)005:1400: pa sogs theg pa'i grangs dang go rim nges bzung
NK131(do)005:1401: mtha' gcig tu byar med pa'i dbang po 'di las
NK131(do)005:1404: mngon par mtho ba nas rnam pa thams cad mkhyen
NK131(do)005:1405: pa'i bar gyi sas bsdus par lam gyi rnam pa'i
NK131(do)005:1406: bgrod byed spyi dang bye brag ji snyed pa thams
NK131(do)005:1407: cad la theg pa'i sgra don gyis khyab pa'i phyir
NK131(do)005:1408: chos kyi rjes gsang sngags snga 'gyur ba rnams theg
NK131(do)005:1409: pa rim dgu'i grangs su bzhed pa dang /
