NK131(do)005:1410: gsar ma'i bzhed pa na yams su bkod pa tsam
NK131(do)005:1411: las de nyid mi 'thad par bzhed pa ma yin
NK131(do)005:1412: pas dpyad pa rnon por rlom pa dag gis grangs
NK131(do)005:1413: kyi dbye bsdu tsam la klan ka mi dgos par
NK131(do)005:1415: bskyed pa'i rim pa gtso bor ston pa ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK131(do)005:1416: rdzogs pa'i rim pa gtso bor ston pa a nu yo ga ste /
NK131(do)005:1417: de yang a nu man chad kyi theg pa 'di
NK131(do)005:1418: rnams sgrub tshul blos byas las ma 'das shing bsgrub
NK131(do)005:1419: bya 'dus byas las ma ldog pas rnal ma'i chos
NK131(do)005:1420: nyid don dam pa'i bden pa mthong ba la khyad
NK131(do)005:1422: nyan rang gis don dam pa'i bden pa rdul rdzas su 'dod pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1423: byang sems kyis bden gnyis res 'jog can tu lta ba dang /
NK131(do)005:1424: kri yas dag bya dag byed kyi rtsol bas 'bras bu don du gnyer ba dang /
NK131(do)005:1425: u b+ha sa lta ba rnal 'byor spyod pa kri ya'i chas 'bras bu sgrub pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1426: rnal 'byor gyis lha dang bdag gnyis su lta ba dang /
NK131(do)005:1427: ma h+aa yo gas bskyed rim blos byas kun brtags dang /
NK131(do)005:1428: rtsa thig rlung gsum la lus ngag yid kyi las
NK131(do)005:1429: bkol pa'i rdzogs rim dpe'i ye shes kyis rjes su
NK131(do)005:1430: dpag pas don gyi ye shes mtshon par 'dod pa
NK131(do)005:1431: dang / u nu yo gas dbyings dang ye shes
NK131(do)005:1432: bskyed bya skyed byed lha'i dkyil 'khor du lta ba
NK131(do)005:1433: rnams rang sa'i shes rab zab pa yin yang rdzogs
NK131(do)005:1434: chen pas gzhal na spang gnyen gyi mtha' la zhen
NK131(do)005:1435: pas gshis kyi bzhugs tshul ji bzhin pa mngon du
NK131(do)005:1436: byed mi nus shing blos byas kyis rig pas rnal
NK131(do)005:1437: ma'i chos nyid la bsgribs par gsungs te /
NK131(do)005:1438: ji skad du kun byed las /
NK131(do)005:1439: nges pa thob pa'i theg pa drug /
NK131(do)005:1440: rdzogs pa chen po'i gos sar bstan //
NK131(do)005:1441: zhes sogs gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK131(do)005:1442: rdzogs pa chen po ni byas chos blo'i grub mtha'
NK131(do)005:1443: kun gyis reg pa'i skabs med pa thog ma nyid
NK131(do)005:1444: nas sems kyi chos nyid ye grol chen por gnas
NK131(do)005:1445: pa'i gshis la yin lugs ltar bzo mi 'chos par
NK131(do)005:1446: gtan la 'bebs pas lam 'og ma dag gis rnam
NK131(do)005:1447: grangs mang pos mngon du bya rgyu'i chos nyid de
NK131(do)005:1448: 'dis 'bad bya rtsol la ma ltos par mngon sum
NK131(do)005:1449: car phog tu mthong bar 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK131(do)005:1450: rdzogs pa'i rim pa thams cad kyi mthar thug yin
NK131(do)005:1451: pas na chen po'i sgra zhugs pa ste rdzogs rim
NK131(do)005:1452: chen po'am / rdzogs pa chen po zhes tha snyad du mdzad pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1453: a nu man chad kyi theg pa brgyad po de
NK131(do)005:1454: rnams lam bden mthar thug gi theg pa gcig po
NK131(do)005:1455: 'di kho nar bgrod pa'i lam stegs su gsungs pa
NK131(do)005:1456: ste / slob dpon in+d+ra b+h+au ti'i rin po che 'khor 'das man ngag las /
NK131(do)005:1457: rang bzhin gyis ni 'od gsal zhing //
NK131(do)005:1458: rdzogs pa chen po'i mthar thug pa //
NK131(do)005:1459: man ngag kun gyi mchog gi mchog /
NK131(do)005:1460: de sgrub thabs su gsungs par zad //
NK131(do)005:1462: de bas de theg pa'i rim par shin tu'ang 'thad
NK131(do)005:1463: pa yin la rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang
NK131(do)005:1464: dngos la sbyor ba'i lam bden thams cad kyi mthar
NK131(do)005:1466: 'dis chos nyid gdod nas dag pa chen po'i gshis
NK131(do)005:1467: kyi bzhugs tshul sgra ji bzhin pa'i mtshar brus par
NK131(do)005:1468: gyur pa la gcar phog tu spros pa'i 'phags pa'i
NK131(do)005:1469: lam bden 'dus ma byas te skad cig nyid la
NK131(do)005:1470: bya rtsol bral ba'i chos nyid la sbyor bar byed
NK131(do)005:1471: pa yin la / de nyid kyi phyir a nu
NK131(do)005:1472: dang a ti gnyis po rnal 'byor chen po kho
NK131(do)005:1473: na'i bskyed rdzogs kyis phye bar bzhed na'ang 'gal ba
NK131(do)005:1474: pa yin la / med de / bla med nyid gzhir byas pa la zab pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1476: shin tu zab pa'i go rim du bzhag na'ang rung ba'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)005:1477: der ma zad a ti yo ga nyid la'ang zab pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1479: shin tu zab pa'i go rim gyis /
NK131(do)005:1481: lta ba rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK131(do)005:1482: chos can lta dang chos nyid lta //
NK131(do)005:1483: a nu man chad rang 'dod pas //
NK131(do)005:1484: chos can nyid la lta lta nas //
NK131(do)005:1485: chos nyid don la rdul reg med //
NK131(do)005:1486: a ti'i rnam pa kha cig gis //
NK131(do)005:1487: 'di nyid phyogs tsam mthong ba med //
NK131(do)005:1488: rdzogs pa chen po thig le'i skor //
NK131(do)005:1489: phyi dang nang dang gsang bas kyang //
NK131(do)005:1490: 'di nyid don la reg pa med //
NK131(do)005:1491: de phyir gsang chen man ngag gi //
NK131(do)005:1492: lta nyid shin tu gsang ba'o //
NK131(do)005:1493: zhes gsungs pa bzhin rdzogs chen nyid la'ang nang gses kyi sgo nas dbye ba /
NK131(do)005:1494: chos thams cad sems nyid las gud na med pas spang bya'i mtha' las grol ba sems kyi sde /
NK131(do)005:1495: chos can thams cad chos nyid kun tu bzang mo'i
NK131(do)005:1496: klong du 'ub chub pas gnyen po'i mtha' las grol
NK131(do)005:1497: ba bya bral klong gi sde /
NK131(do)005:1498: yin lugs ltar gtan la 'bebs pas spang gnyen gnyis
NK131(do)005:1499: ka'i mtha' las grol ba zab pa man ngag gi
NK131(do)005:1501: phyi ma la'ang lus dang 'dra ba phyi skor /
NK131(do)005:1504: thams cad rdzogs pa'i skyes bu dang 'dra ba yang
NK131(do)005:1505: gsang bla na med pa'i skor dang bzhir phye ba
NK131(do)005:1506: yod de / de dag rnams kyang snga ma snga
NK131(do)005:1507: ma las phyi ma phyi ma rim gyis zab cing
NK131(do)005:1508: rgya che ba'i tshul gyis gong ma'i shes rab kyis
NK131(do)005:1509: 'og ma sun dbyung nas mthar bsam gyis mi khyab
NK131(do)005:1510: pa'i chos nyid kyis chos thams cad zad pa'i grub
NK131(do)005:1511: mtha' gdod ma'i zad sa chen por skyel so bya
NK131(do)005:1512: yod de / da pa ste / gsang skor man
NK131(do)005:1513: gyi rdzogs chen pa 'di dag gis kyang chos nyid
NK131(do)005:1514: yid dpyod kyi lam du lus pa las yang gsang
NK131(do)005:1516: de nyid sgom med khregs chod kyis grol sa'i ka dag chen po la sbyor ba dang /
NK131(do)005:1517: sgom yod thod rgal gyis mngon sum dbang po'i yul
NK131(do)005:1518: du ngo 'phrod pas yid dpyod lkog gyur du ma
NK131(do)005:1519: lus pas gegs dang gol sa las grol bas khyad
NK131(do)005:1521: de nyid la byar med rtsol bral du gnad du bsnun pas nyams gong 'phel du byed cing /
NK131(do)005:1522: tshad thog tu phebs nas blo dang chos su btags
NK131(do)005:1523: pa'i 'khrul snang gi rgyal khams thams cad zad pa'am
NK131(do)005:1524: nub nas ye shes kyi rgyal khams chen por la
NK131(do)005:1525: ma zlos kyi bar du rim pas bogs dbyung nas
NK131(do)005:1526: mngon du bya rgyu ches mang ba'i phyir theg pa'i
NK131(do)005:1528: gang gi tshe mthar phyin pa na nyams kyi 'phel
NK131(do)005:1529: pa'ang zad nas gzhi'i 'od gsal longs sku chen po'i
NK131(do)005:1530: nang dbyings gzhon nu bum pa sku'i dkyil 'khor du
NK131(do)005:1531: shel 'od nang du sdud pa ltar zad dang mi
NK131(do)005:1532: skye ba'i ye shes chen po mngon du byas pa'i
NK131(do)005:1533: tshe / 'di la snga 'gyur rdzogs chen pas 'khrul
NK131(do)005:1534: ba'i chos kyis dag tshul la btags pas blo zad
NK131(do)005:1535: chos zad ces tha snyad byed cing /
NK131(do)005:1537: sems ni nam zhig gyur pa na /
NK131(do)005:1538: theg pa med cing bgrod pa'ang med /
NK131(do)005:1539: ces pa'i don la ji bzhin pa 'byor pa yin la /
NK131(do)005:1540: des na a ti yo ga ye shes yin gyi
NK131(do)005:1541: theg pa min zhes gsungs pa ni 'dus pa sogs
NK131(do)005:1542: kyi rnal 'byor bzhi'i rim pa'i a ti yo ga
NK131(do)005:1543: la dgongs nas gsungs par snang ba'i phyir des rdzogs
NK131(do)005:1544: pa chen po a ti yo ga theg pa min
NK131(do)005:1546: gal te smra ba po gzhan gyis de la bsams nas brjod na'ang min par dka' ste /
NK131(do)005:1547: brjod byar ltos nas ye shes dang /
NK131(do)005:1548: rjod byed la ltos nas theg par bzhag pa byar yod de /
NK131(do)005:1549: brjod bya rjod byed la mtshan du btags pa sher
NK131(do)005:1550: phyin ston pa'i sde snod la shes rab kyi pha
NK131(do)005:1551: rol tu phyin pa zhes smos pa bzhin te /
NK131(do)005:1553: shes rab pha rol phyin gnyis med //
NK131(do)005:1554: ye shes de ni de bzhin gshegs //
NK131(do)005:1555: bsgrub bya don de dang ldan pas //
NK131(do)005:1556: gzhung lam dag la de sgras bstan //
NK131(do)005:1558: ye shes yin na de nyid theg pa'ang yin te
NK131(do)005:1559: ye shes rtogs byed kyi thabs sam rgyur gyur pa
NK131(do)005:1560: la theg pa zhes brjod de ye shes mthong ba
NK131(do)005:1561: nye ring la ltos nas theg pa che chung rgyu
NK131(do)005:1562: 'bras kyi theg pa so sor phye ba'i phyir /
NK131(do)005:1563: sangs rgyas phal po che las /
NK131(do)005:1564: ye shes kyi theg pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1565: theg pa chen po la gzhol ba'i sems kyis dge ba'i rtsa ba de dag yongs su bsngo'o //
NK131(do)005:1567: rab rtsal rnam gnon gyis zhus pa las /
NK131(do)005:1568: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes ni theg pa chen po'o //
NK131(do)005:1569: zhes ched du bka' stsal pa'i phyir chos kyi rje'i
NK131(do)005:1570: drang don dgongs pa can gyi gsung la blo dman
NK131(do)005:1571: gzhan gyis nges don du 'khrul par mi bya bar
NK131(do)005:1572: ji ltar bka' stsal ba'i don nyid la mnyam par
NK131(do)005:1573: bzhag dgos so // rigs pas kyang 'grub ste /
NK131(do)005:1574: rta dang ldan pa'i shing rta la rta'i shing rta
NK131(do)005:1575: zhes brjod pa bzhin du ye shes de dang ldan
NK131(do)005:1576: pa'i theg pa la a ti yo ga'i theg pa
NK131(do)005:1577: zhes brjod pa la klan ka ci'i phyir 'jug /
NK131(do)005:1578: des na gsang sngags snga 'gyur pa la thun mong
NK131(do)005:1579: ma yin par grags pa'i yo ga rnam pa gsum
NK131(do)005:1580: gyi brjod bya zab la rgya che ba dus gsum
NK131(do)005:1581: gyi de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pa'i dgongs
NK131(do)005:1582: pa'i zhe phug sa rgyud sde 'og ma phyi rgyud
NK131(do)005:1583: sde gsum du ming tsam yang ma grags pa'i mthar
NK131(do)005:1584: thug gi skyel so gang yin pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1585: rjod byed tshig gi rgyud rdzogs chen rang la'ang 'bum
NK131(do)005:1586: phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi yod par gsungs pa las
NK131(do)005:1587: gangs ri'i ljongs 'dir chos rgyal lo pan gyi thugs
NK131(do)005:1588: bskyed rmad byung gi sku drin dang /
NK131(do)005:1589: dus de'i gdul bya'i bsod nams kyi bgo skal las
NK131(do)005:1590: cha shas tsam zhig lkog chos kho nar bsgyur ba
NK131(do)005:1591: gsang nas nyams su blangs pas dngos grub mchog thob
NK131(do)005:1592: pa mang zhig byung ba'i rjes su bod rnams kyis
NK131(do)005:1593: bsod nams ma yin pa dus su smin pa dang
NK131(do)005:1594: / gdul bya'i snod kyi rten 'brel re zhig rdzogs
NK131(do)005:1595: pa 'grigs nas glang dar ma 'u dum btsan gyis
NK131(do)005:1596: rgyal bstan rin po che la skabs btsal ba nas
NK131(do)005:1597: bzung rtogs pa don gyi chos 'khor yo ga rnam
NK131(do)005:1598: pa gsum gyi bstan pa sbas pa'i yul rnams dang
NK131(do)005:1599: / / yul phran khol bu rnams su mi mngon
NK131(do)005:1600: par bzhugs pas bstan pa phyi dar gyi dus su
NK131(do)005:1601: mkhas blun phal mo che'i mdun sar ma 'grims pa'i
NK131(do)005:1602: / / rgyu mtshan dang / rgya gar gyi pan
NK131(do)005:1603: grub rnams gsang ba la thugs sgam pas yongs su
NK131(do)005:1604: ma grags pa tsam la brten nas phyis kyi lo
NK131(do)005:1605: ts+aa pa 'ga' zhig gis rdzogs chen rgya gar du
NK131(do)005:1606: ma grags par bsams pa'i rgyu yang de dag las
NK131(do)005:1608: des na rnal 'byor bzhi'i rim pa dang nang pa
NK131(do)005:1609: bskyed rdzogs gsum ming mthun pa la dgongs nas ngo
NK131(do)005:1610: bo gcig par bsgrubs nas de la theg pa'i go
NK131(do)005:1611: rim mi 'thad pa'i gtan tshigs bkod kyang 'grub par
NK131(do)005:1612: dka' ste / bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi brjod don rnal
NK131(do)005:1613: ma'i de bzhin nyid rtogs pa la thabs mi zab
NK131(do)005:1614: pa dang zab pa dang ches shin tu zab pa'i
NK131(do)005:1615: khyad par gong ma gong ma'i shes rab kyis 'byed
NK131(do)005:1616: pas theg pa'i go rim du bzhag par byar phod
NK131(do)005:1617: dka' ste / cing / rjod byed sgra tshig gi
NK131(do)005:1618: rgyud sde'i rnam grangs kyang dpag par dka' ba zhig
NK131(do)005:1619: bzhugs par gsungs pa'i phyir brjod bya rjod byed kyis
NK131(do)005:1620: shin tu tha dad pa yin no //
NK131(do)005:1621: gnyis pa zur gyis phog par 'dod pa sel ba la'ang gsum ste /
NK131(do)005:1622: rdzogs chen la h+aa shang chen po'i chos lugs 'dres par 'dod pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1623: 'bras bu'i mthar thug 'od gsal du mi 'thad par 'dod pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1624: gter nas byung ba'i chos kyi brgyud pa rdo rje
NK131(do)005:1625: 'chang la snyeg pa mi 'thad par 'dod pa'i dogs
NK131(do)005:1627: da lta'i phyag rgya chen po dang //
NK131(do)005:1628: rgya nag lugs kyi rdzogs chen la //
NK131(do)005:1630: phal rgya nag chos lugs yin /
NK131(do)005:1632: 'di la gser gyi thur ma las /
NK131(do)005:1633: rgya nag mkhan po'i chos lugs la rdzogs chen gyi
NK131(do)005:1634: ming 'dogs pa khong rang gi lugs la med kyang
NK131(do)005:1635: a ti pas thabs kyi cha mi dgos pa de
NK131(do)005:1636: ltar khas blangs na der song zhes phul ba'o //
NK131(do)005:1637: zhes gsungs pa de yang dgongs gzhi rim gyis pa'i
NK131(do)005:1638: lugs shing rta chen po'i rjes 'brangs tshad mar sgrub
NK131(do)005:1640: cig car par grags pa nges don du 'khrul pa
NK131(do)005:1641: med kyang dbang rnon gyi lam yin pa'i phyir dbang
NK131(do)005:1642: po rno rtul thams cad der 'jug pa dgag pa'i
NK131(do)005:1643: phyir dgongs pa can gyi gsung du nges so //
NK131(do)005:1644: 'on kyang phyis su byis pa ka kha shes pa
NK131(do)005:1645: yan chad kyis h+aa shang gi chos log ces mu
NK131(do)005:1646: stegs dang kla klo tsam du nor ba'i khungs byed
NK131(do)005:1648: thog mar rgya nag mkhan po'i chos de nor ba yang dag pa yin min la dpyad dgos pas /
NK131(do)005:1649: chos de'i khungs bshad pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1650: de nyid skyon med par bstan pa'o //
NK131(do)005:1652: rgya nag gi yul du bstan pa thog mar phebs
NK131(do)005:1653: pa'i dus ni h+aan gyi ming d+h+ai rgyal po yung
NK131(do)005:1654: phing gi rmi lam du de bzhin gshegs pas byin
NK131(do)005:1655: gyis brlabs pa'i ltas byung bas rgyu byas /
NK131(do)005:1656: sngon gyi rgyal po te 'u co 'u dbang gi
NK131(do)005:1657: dus kyi bstan pa dar bar 'gyur ba'i lung bstan
NK131(do)005:1658: gyi yi ge rnyed pas gsol btab nas 'phags yul
NK131(do)005:1659: du chos 'tshol ba'i pho nya btang ba dang /
NK131(do)005:1660: dgra bcom pa ma tang+gi dang /
NK131(do)005:1661: pan+di ta h+pha la ra gnyis byon nas bstan pa'i
NK131(do)005:1662: dbu brnyes de nas bzung rim gyis theg pa che
NK131(do)005:1663: chung gi sde snod dang pan+di ta shin tu mang
NK131(do)005:1664: ba phebs shing bstan pa 'dzin spel nus pa'i h+aa
NK131(do)005:1665: shang mkhas shing grub pa shin tu mang bar byon
NK131(do)005:1676: thang sogs nas de dag gi bar du rgyal bstan
NK131(do)005:1677: rin po che rgyu'i theg pa gtso bor dar ba
NK131(do)005:1678: ma nyams shing shin tu 'phel ba'i rgyun las /
NK131(do)005:1679: h+aa shang byang chub sems dpa' chen po mngon shes
NK131(do)005:1680: dang ting nge 'dzin la dbang 'byor pa'ang bgrangs kyis
NK131(do)005:1681: mi lang pa byon nas bstan pa bskyangs pa'i gtam
NK131(do)005:1682: rgyas par spro bar nus mod kyang yi ges 'jigs
NK131(do)005:1683: pas mi spro'o // de las 'dul ba'i bstan pa ni 'phags pa dge 'dun go cha dang /
NK131(do)005:1684: rig 'dzin ku m+aa ra'i rjes su 'jug pa'i bshad
NK131(do)005:1685: pa dang phyag len rgyun shin tu gtsang ba deng
NK131(do)005:1686: sang gi bar du dar la /
NK131(do)005:1687: gsang sngags la ni rgyud sde 'og ma ci rigs par nyan bshad kyi srol byung mod /
NK131(do)005:1688: bla med spyi dang khyad par rnal 'byor ma'i rgyud
NK131(do)005:1689: ni gdul bya'i blo la ma shong bas rgyal po
NK131(do)005:1690: rnams kyi bkas bcad nas srol tshugs par ma nus
NK131(do)005:1691: so // pha rol phyin pa'i gzhung la /
NK131(do)005:1692: rgyal chen spyod pa'i brgyud pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1693: zab mo lta ba'i brgyud pa /
NK131(do)005:1694: sgrub rgyud don gyi brgyud pa ste /
NK131(do)005:1695: bka' srol gsum yod pa la so so'i brgyud pa'ang
NK131(do)005:1696: bar ma chad kyi khungs rnam par dag pa dang
NK131(do)005:1697: ldan zhing de yang bod rnams bzhin du mkhas pa
NK131(do)005:1698: so so'i blo la shar tshod kyi bshad srol dang
NK131(do)005:1699: lag len byed sa med pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1700: chos rgyun de yang rang rang sngon gyi brgyud srol
NK131(do)005:1701: gang 'dzin pa de las gzhan mang po 'dres mar
NK131(do)005:1702: mi byed pa sogs kyis shin tu rnam par dag
NK131(do)005:1703: pa'i brgyud pa dang ldan pa'o //
NK131(do)005:1704: de la rgya chen spyod pa'i brgyud pa ni /
NK131(do)005:1705: rgyal tshab ma pham pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1710: 'di las rgya'i slob dpon thang zan tsang gis zhus
NK131(do)005:1711: nas rgya yul du mdo dgongs pa nges 'grel dang
NK131(do)005:1713: byams chos lnga sogs bka' dang bstan bcos shin tu mang ba bsgyur cing /
NK131(do)005:1714: lta sgom spyod gsum gyi sgo nas bka' tha ma'i bstan pa rgya cher spel lo //
NK131(do)005:1715: zab mo lta ba'i brgyud pa ni /
NK131(do)005:1721: rgya yi slob dpon ye shes dpal /
NK131(do)005:1723: de la sa h+aa shang chen po ti zhes d+aa
NK131(do)005:1724: shi la brgyud de 'di ni rgya nag gi yul
NK131(do)005:1725: du zab mo lta ba'i shing rta chen por gyur
NK131(do)005:1726: te mngon shes dang byang chub sems la dbang 'byor
NK131(do)005:1727: bas phyogs der sangs rgyas gnyis pa lta bu'i phrin
NK131(do)005:1729: gsung rab spyi la dus tshigs lnga'i khog 'bums pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1730: khyad par zab mo lta ba'i gnas la sher phyin dang mdo pad dkar sogs bka' dang /
NK131(do)005:1731: dgongs 'grel rtsa shes 'bum t+ai ka sogs la 'chad nyan dang /
NK131(do)005:1732: bstan bcos kyang shin tu mang bar mang bar mdzad /
NK131(do)005:1733: tun min te cig car 'jug pa'i sgo dang /
NK131(do)005:1734: tsi yan min te rim gyis 'jug pa'i sgo dang /
NK131(do)005:1735: b+ai mi ste gsang ba thun mong min pa'i sgo dang /
NK131(do)005:1739: rnam par dbye ba'i sgo dang /
NK131(do)005:1740: yongs su rdzogs pa'i sgo ste 'jug sgo brgyad kyi
NK131(do)005:1741: srol tshugs par mdzad pa sogs bstan pa la mchog
NK131(do)005:1743: gsum pa sgrub rgyud don gyi brgyud pa 'dir tsung min zhes bya ste /
NK131(do)005:1744: bka'i brgyud par bsgyur du rung ba /
NK131(do)005:1745: nyams len byin rlabs brgyud pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1746: rig stong phyag rgya chen por yang bod chog pa snying po don gyi bstan par grags te /
NK131(do)005:1747: rje btsun t+aa ra n+aa tha'i rgya gar chos 'byung du /
NK131(do)005:1748: mgon po klu sgrub kyis ar+ya de ba la snying
NK131(do)005:1749: po don gyi bstan pa gtad nas dpal gyi ri
NK131(do)005:1750: la gshegs so // zhes gsungs pa'ang 'di la dgongs pa ste /
NK131(do)005:1751: don gyi bstan pa 'di shin tu zab cing rgya
NK131(do)005:1752: che ba nyid kyi phyir thun mong gi spyod yul
NK131(do)005:1753: las 'das pas blo gros chen po dang ldan pa
NK131(do)005:1754: la tshig brgyud du ston dgos pa'i ched du ste
NK131(do)005:1755: / tshig spyi'i bstan pa'i gtad rabs tsam ni ma yin no //
NK131(do)005:1756: de lta bu de rgya nag gi yul du byung ba'i tshul ni /
NK131(do)005:1757: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa /
NK131(do)005:1760: dgra bcom pa sha na'i gos can /
NK131(do)005:1762: de las 'phags pa d+hi d+hi ka dang /
NK131(do)005:1763: nyi ma gung pa gnyis las /
NK131(do)005:1764: d+hi d+hi ka nas dgra bcom pa nag po /
NK131(do)005:1789: de nas byang chub chos mchog ste slob dpon 'di
NK131(do)005:1790: 'od srungs nas bzung gtad rabs nyi shu rtsa brgyad
NK131(do)005:1791: pa yin la / khong nyid kyis 'phags yul du
NK131(do)005:1792: sna tshogs bshes gnyen phyi ma la bstan pa gtad
NK131(do)005:1794: ki'ang nan gyi yul du li'ang u d+d+h+ai rgyal po
NK131(do)005:1795: dang mjal nas rgyal po dang dge bshes 'ga' zhig
NK131(do)005:1797: ji skad du 'phags pa sdud pa las /
NK131(do)005:1798: ji ltar dug dang 'dres pa'i kha zas bzang za ba /
NK131(do)005:1799: dkar po'i chos la dmigs pa'ang de 'drar rgyal bas gsungs /
NK131(do)005:1801: rgyal po de dad pa dang gtong ba sogs kyis bsod nams gsog pa la snying stobs che yang /
NK131(do)005:1802: zab mo'i don la mi mos shing rang gi mdzad pa la rlom sems yod pa dang /
NK131(do)005:1803: mchod gnas phal mo che yang zab mo'i don la
NK131(do)005:1804: lta ba'i shes rab bogs ma thon par thos pa'i
NK131(do)005:1805: yon tan tsam gyis mngon par khengs pa mang bas
NK131(do)005:1806: de dag zab mo'i chos nyid la bkri ba'i slad
NK131(do)005:1807: du shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i gnas
NK131(do)005:1808: lugs sgra ji bzhin pa drang thad du bstan /
NK131(do)005:1810: nyams len bzang shos rnams la bya ba ngan pa
NK131(do)005:1811: thongs shig gsungs pa'i dgongs pa ltar spyod pa'i mtha'
NK131(do)005:1812: la zhen pas mi 'ching ba'i thabs la bkri bar
NK131(do)005:1813: mdzad pa na / sngon du zab mo'i gnas la
NK131(do)005:1814: blo gros ma phyogs pa'i rgyus thams cad ha las
NK131(do)005:1815: mdzad pa na / / bod du lugs 'di chad
NK131(do)005:1816: ltar 'khrul pa'i gtam de'ang thog mar rgya nag tu
NK131(do)005:1817: mdzad pa na / / byung ste / mkhas par
NK131(do)005:1818: rlom pa rnams kyang blo la ma shong nas chad
NK131(do)005:1819: lta mkhan du rtog cing skur par gyur /
NK131(do)005:1820: rgyal po la ngo so ma mdzad pas de nyid
NK131(do)005:1821: ma dga' ba'i rkyen gyis kyang thams cad kyis btang
NK131(do)005:1822: snyoms su byas / slob dpon gyis der gdul bya
NK131(do)005:1823: dus la ma babs par gzigs nas byang yu gur
NK131(do)005:1825: ki'ang gi klung chen po la rdzu 'phrul gyi bya
NK131(do)005:1826: bas brgal ba dang dmag dpon gru la zhon nas
NK131(do)005:1827: 'gro ba zhig gis mthong nas dad pa thob /
NK131(do)005:1828: gtam de rgya nag lho pa rnams kyis thos nas
NK131(do)005:1829: 'gyod kyang byi la shor ba'i skang khung du sang
NK131(do)005:1830: / h+aa shang ha'i kha zhes bya ba sngon gyi
NK131(do)005:1831: smon lam rgya chen po sad par nye ba zhig
NK131(do)005:1832: gis gtam de thos pa tsam gyis dad pa'i spu
NK131(do)005:1833: long g.yo bar gyur nas yu gur gyi phyogs su
NK131(do)005:1834: tshol du byon par slob dpon zhoo'u lin za'i dgon
NK131(do)005:1835: par 'dug skad thos der mkhas pa bo d+h+ai ru
NK131(do)005:1836: tsi sogs rgya dkar nag gi mkhas pa mang pos
NK131(do)005:1837: chos kyi bya ba mdzad cing 'dug na slob dpon
NK131(do)005:1838: chos mchog gi snod du rung ba'i slob ma bsgugs
NK131(do)005:1839: cing lo dgu'i bar du sbas pa'i brtul zhugs kyis
NK131(do)005:1840: gnas pa zhig la dus gzhan zhig tu h+aa'i khe
NK131(do)005:1841: / dang / yu gur gyi ban+de gsum bcas bzhi
NK131(do)005:1842: pos slob dpon dang 'phrad nas skal ba mchog dang
NK131(do)005:1843: ldan pa ni hu'i khe nyid yin la /
NK131(do)005:1844: 'on kyang de dag la chos ston tshul ni /
NK131(do)005:1845: dred po go yul du shor ba'i nyen 'byung bar
NK131(do)005:1846: dgongs te ka kha slob pa ltar gang yang mi
NK131(do)005:1847: slob ste / brda bstan pas dris pa la lan
NK131(do)005:1848: ldog pa'i tshul du phyag rgya chen po'i man ngag
NK131(do)005:1849: byin nas don la bsam du bcug /
NK131(do)005:1850: bsam byung gi shes rab brtas pa na bsgom du
NK131(do)005:1851: bcug pa sogs bshad rgyud kyi go yul tsam min
NK131(do)005:1852: par kha nang du log nas sgom pa'i don kho
NK131(do)005:1853: na la skyor bar mdzad pa'i lo rgyus 'di ni
NK131(do)005:1854: / jo bo chen po'i zhal nas /
NK131(do)005:1855: thos pas mi shes bsgoms pas shes //
NK131(do)005:1856: zhes gsungs pa dang mthun la /
NK131(do)005:1857: de tsam du ma zad theg pa chen po'i sgom
NK131(do)005:1858: byung gi gtam thams cad gnas tshul de las ma
NK131(do)005:1860: chos 'di ni tshig dang yi ge las shin tu 'das pa /
NK131(do)005:1861: sgra dang rtog ge'i yul ma yin pa /
NK131(do)005:1862: dpe dang gtan tshigs kyis gtan la mi phebs pa /
NK131(do)005:1863: zhes rnam pa kun tu bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)005:1864: des na hu'i kha gcig pus de kho na nyid
NK131(do)005:1865: kyi don dang mjal zhing gzhan gsum pos kyang don
NK131(do)005:1867: slob dpon gyis snga ma de'i rgyud smin par gzigs
NK131(do)005:1868: nas snying po don gyi bstan pa gtad nas bdag
NK131(do)005:1869: gis gtsang klung brgal ba'i dus bardzisa pa'i 'dam bu
NK131(do)005:1870: la lo ma lnga yod pa'i rten 'brel gyis khyed
NK131(do)005:1871: las chig brgyud kyi gtad rabs lnga pa nas mang
NK131(do)005:1872: por 'phel / de nas tshugs thub kyi sde pa
NK131(do)005:1873: lngar 'gyur zhes lung bstan gyi gtam bzhag nas de
NK131(do)005:1875: phyis rgya gar nas 'ongs pa'i 'grul pa 'ga' zhig

NK131(do)005:1880: do // de'ang slob dpon hu'i khe d+aa tsu tshan shing /

NK131(do)005:1882: da'u sin d+aa i chan shi'/
NK131(do)005:1883: hung gzhin d+aa ma na chad shi /
NK131(do)005:1884: l+au tsu hu'i ning d+aa ki lan chag shi'/
NK131(do)005:1885: nan yo hu wa'i bzhad chan shi'/
NK131(do)005:1886: ma tsu d+aa 'u yi chan shi'am /
NK131(do)005:1887: pe tang mi 'o'u shi chan shi'/
NK131(do)005:1888: hu'ang po'i shi yu chan shi'/
NK131(do)005:1889: lin gyi i shu'ana chan shi'/
NK131(do)005:1890: de nyid the ba'i mi rabs sum cu rtsa bzhi dang /
NK131(do)005:1891: brgyud pa'i rabs slob dpon chos mchog nas /
NK131(do)005:1892: thi yo'u me'i ming ting chan shing la thug gi
NK131(do)005:1893: bar rabs bzhi bcu zhe bzhi byon pa rnams thugs
NK131(do)005:1894: nas thugs su brgyud pa'i nyams myong byin rlabs kyi
NK131(do)005:1896: zhes rgya nag tu dam pa'i chos byung ba'i tshul
NK131(do)005:1897: gyi gtams yang dag pa tshad mar gyur ba las
NK131(do)005:1898: ji ltar 'byung ba bzhin bkod pa ste /
NK131(do)005:1899: de'ang bod du bstan pa dar ba dang gung sgrig na /
NK131(do)005:1900: don brgyud 'di 'phags yul nas rgya nag tu thog
NK131(do)005:1901: mar phebs pa'i skabs kyi rgya nag lho pa ki'ang
NK131(do)005:1902: nan gyi li'ang u d+h+ai rgyal po dgung lo bzhi
NK131(do)005:1904: de'i rgyal rabs bzhi par rgyal srid then gyis blangs /
NK131(do)005:1905: 'di'i rabs ci tsam byung gsal ka mi 'dug na'ang /
NK131(do)005:1906: mthar rgyal srid yu gur gyi blon po'i rigs las
NK131(do)005:1907: je 'u'i blon po yang ki'ana gyis blangs pa'i rgyal
NK131(do)005:1909: sus kyi mi rabs gsum gyi lo bsdoms pa nyi
NK131(do)005:1910: shu rtsa dgu'i rjes su thang li yu'ana gyis thob
NK131(do)005:1911: ste / li'u yan 'di'i sras che ba thang tha'i
NK131(do)005:1912: tsu rgyal po bod rnams kyis seng ge btsan por
NK131(do)005:1913: bod pa bod rgyal srong btsan sgam po dang dus
NK131(do)005:1914: mtshungs te wen ching kung cu'i yab yin no //
NK131(do)005:1915: des na thang gi rgyal rabs thog ma dang bod
NK131(do)005:1916: rgyal byang chub sems dpa' rnams dus mtshungs par shes
NK131(do)005:1917: dgos te / rags pa tsam du theg gi dus
NK131(do)005:1918: dang bod rgyal tho ri snyan shal 'grig gam snyam
NK131(do)005:1919: pa ni bdag gi rnam rtog ste 'phros don no
NK131(do)005:1921: bod kyi ljongs 'dir btsad po khri srong lde'u btsan
NK131(do)005:1922: gyis 'phags pa'i yul nas +aa ts+aar+ya bo d+hi sa
NK131(do)005:1923: t+wa dang / pad+ma 'byung gnas sogs spyan drangs nas
NK131(do)005:1924: rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che spel bar mdzad
NK131(do)005:1925: pa'i snga rol tu rgya nag gi slob dpon mang
NK131(do)005:1926: po spyan drangs nas theg pa che chung gi sde
NK131(do)005:1927: snod mang po bshad bsgyur gyis gtan la phab /
NK131(do)005:1928: phyis shig tu mkhan po byang chub sems dpa' sku
NK131(do)005:1929: dbang po'i 'og tu rgya'i slob dpon theg pa chen
NK131(do)005:1930: po par grags zhig byon pa'i thugs su sangs rgyas
NK131(do)005:1931: phal po che'i sde snod bzhugs pa lda ch+aa na
NK131(do)005:1932: shi lo lo ts+aa byas te bsgyur /
NK131(do)005:1933: skabs 'dir mkhan po'i slob ma rnams la tsi yan men dang /
NK131(do)005:1934: bsam gtan mkhan po la ton mes tu btags pa
NK131(do)005:1935: ni bod rnams kyis rang bzor nges te rgya nag
NK131(do)005:1936: tu grags pa dang ni mi mtshungs so //
NK131(do)005:1937: bsam gtan mkhan por grags pa de ni cung min
NK131(do)005:1938: gyi bka' srol 'dzin pa man ngag myong la gtso
NK131(do)005:1940: gong du smos pa'i tsung min gyi gtad rabs lnga
NK131(do)005:1941: pa man chad cig tu byung bar shes la rgya
NK131(do)005:1942: nag gi lo rgyus su slob dpon 'di'i gsal ka
NK131(do)005:1944: gang ltar pha rol phyin pa'i man ngag gi don
NK131(do)005:1945: brgyud kyi gdams pa tshig dang yi ge las 'das

NK131(do)005:1952: bor byed pa'i mkhas pa rnams kyi thugs su ma

NK131(do)005:1957: shang dang zhal 'dzom pa na ka ma la sh+ai
NK131(do)005:1958: las phyag shing klad du lan gsum bskor ba'i brdas
NK131(do)005:1959: khams gsum du 'khor ba'i rgyu dris pa /

NK131(do)005:1964: sar bzhugs pa rtsod pa med de so so yang
NK131(do)005:1965: dag pa'i rig pa bzhi la dbang 'byor bas so
NK131(do)005:1966: // de nas ka sh+ai dpon slob dang bsam gtan
NK131(do)005:1967: mkhan po shag 'gyed pa la zhugs pa na rgya
NK131(do)005:1968: gar pa dpon slob ni thun mong du yongs su

NK131(do)005:1971: spyod pa dus tshod dang 'brel ba'i chos la gtso bor mdzad pa /

NK131(do)005:1974: pa dang / de nyid dgag sgrub kyi spros pa

NK131(do)005:1987: pa dang / su bzhud do // bo ni /
NK131(do)005:1988: dang / pa tsam mo // de la blo gzu

NK131(do)005:1991: tshe spyod pa'i mtha' la zhen pa rang sa'i sgrib
NK131(do)005:1992: pa rngams po cher 'gyur bas de dang der zhen
NK131(do)005:1993: na 'ching bar bstan pa ni nges don gyi sde

NK131(do)005:1995: thug tu nges par dmigs pa can gyi dge rtsa
NK131(do)005:1996: sbyin sogs thams cad de dang de'i tshu rol dang
NK131(do)005:1997: / dmigs pa med pa'i shes rab kyis zin pa'i
NK131(do)005:1998: zag pa med pa'i dge rtsa sbyin sogs drug gi
NK131(do)005:1999: pha rol tu phyin par gsungs na /

NK131(do)005:2001: dmigs pa med pa'i chos nyid drang thad du ston
NK131(do)005:2002: pa'i gnas skabs thams cad du don 'di las ma
NK131(do)005:2003: 'das pas na bsam gtan mkhan po rjes 'brangs dang
NK131(do)005:2004: bcas pa'i rang bzo ma yin par shes par bya
NK131(do)005:2005: zhing / des rang gi rang mi dge ba'i rtog
NK131(do)005:2006: pa gang yang rung bas gnas lugs yang dag pa
NK131(do)005:2007: mthong ba la sgrib par byed pa ni rtsod pa

NK131(do)005:2009: phyogs snga ma nyid dang ro gcig pa yin te

NK131(do)005:2012: mkhas pas der ni gnas mi bya //

NK131(do)005:2014: rtog la bye brag ci zhig yod //
NK131(do)005:2015: rten gyi dbye ba la brten pa'i //

NK131(do)005:2023: drang ba'i phyir de dang phyogs mthun tsam bstan pa
NK131(do)005:2024: las rang nyid kyi bzhed pa'i snying po nges pa'i
NK131(do)005:2025: don de las rnam pa kun tu mi 'da' ba
NK131(do)005:2026: tshad mas gsal bar byas pa yin zhing /
NK131(do)005:2027: spyir yang slob dpon 'di dang bsam gtan mkhan po
NK131(do)005:2028: rtsod pa byung ba tsam gyis de dang de'i chos
NK131(do)005:2029: lugs dag dri ma can du 'dod mi nus te
NK131(do)005:2030: don la gnod byed tshad ma med pa'i phyir dang
NK131(do)005:2031: / gal te slob dpon bsam gtan mkhan pos chos
NK131(do)005:2032: kyi dbyings 'dus ma byas kyi bzhugs tshul drang thad
NK131(do)005:2033: du ston pa de nyid las dang po pa la'ang
NK131(do)005:2034: thog ma nyid du bstan pas cung zad nongs so

NK131(do)005:2037: tshod la ltos nas cung zad nongs par 'gyur srid
NK131(do)005:2038: kyang de pa dag gi chos de rtsa ba bcas
NK131(do)005:2039: pa thams cad skyon can du mi 'gyur te /
NK131(do)005:2040: gang zag rang gi blo skyon tsam du nges pa'i phyir dang /
NK131(do)005:2041: der ma zad gdul bya so so'i blo tshod dang
NK131(do)005:2042: ma mthun pas theg pa chen po'i lta sgom spyod
NK131(do)005:2043: pa lam 'og ma pa dag gi blor ma shong
NK131(do)005:2044: nas rtsod pa 'byung ba ni chos nyid de /
NK131(do)005:2045: nyan thos rnams kyis theg chen bka' ma yin par
NK131(do)005:2046: 'dod pa la de nyid bkar sgrub pa mdo sde
NK131(do)005:2047: rgyan du 'byung ba dang gsang sngags bkar sgrub pa
NK131(do)005:2048: rgya gzhung du ma las 'byung ba dang /
NK131(do)005:2049: zla ba grags pas ngo bo nyid med pa'i dbu ma dang /
NK131(do)005:2050: tsan+d+ra go mis rnam rig dbu ma'i phyogs bzung nas
NK131(do)005:2051: lo bdun gyi bar du brgal brtag mdzad pa sogs
NK131(do)005:2052: kyis gzhung de dang de skyon can du bsgrubs nas
NK131(do)005:2053: 'dor ba'i mi rung ba bzhin no //

NK131(do)005:2055: la grags pa zhig byung phyin gzu bo'i blos zhib
NK131(do)005:2056: mor brtag dpyad bya ba'i skabs med par /

NK131(do)005:2058: thams cad la spyi khyab tu sngar nas chags pas
NK131(do)005:2059: mkhas par grags pa rnams la'ang de'i shan gyis gos
NK131(do)005:2060: pas sam phyis kyi rtog ger goms pa rnams /
NK131(do)005:2061: bsam gtan mkhan po'i chos lugs dang /
NK131(do)005:2062: de dang mthun pa'i chos skad gang du mchis pa
NK131(do)005:2063: thams cad kyang chos log dri ma can du bsams
NK131(do)005:2064: nas thos na'ang rna ba 'gebs pa tsam du lta
NK131(do)005:2065: bas don du theg pa chen po'i chos spang ba'i
NK131(do)005:2066: rtsa ltung drug pa dang dgu pa 'bad nas khur
NK131(do)005:2067: du bzhes mkhan mang po zhig 'byung gin snang yang
NK131(do)005:2068: / mnyam gzhag tu rnam par mi rtog pa ni
NK131(do)005:2069: theg chen gyi mdo dang rgyud sde thams cad kyi
NK131(do)005:2070: dgongs par rtsod pa med pa /

NK131(do)005:2074: gang zhig 'du shes mi gnas sems par mi gnas la //

NK131(do)005:2119: bzhin yid byed kyi sgo nas bsam byung gi dpyad
NK131(do)005:2120: pas rten 'byung gi de kho na nyid la nges

NK131(do)005:2126: theg chen gyi rten 'brel rigs pa sogs shing rta
NK131(do)005:2127: chen po pa dag gis bkral ba'i dgongs pa ni
NK131(do)005:2128: rjes thob tu lhag mthong de nyid kyi tshul la
NK131(do)005:2129: blos nges pa bskyed pa'i phyir dang lung rigs kyis
NK131(do)005:2130: sgro 'dogs gcod pa'i skabs su sbyor bar shes dgos

NK131(do)005:2159: gnyug ma'i chos nyid la reg pa'i skabs med de
NK131(do)005:2161: 'od srungs bdag tu 'dzin pa ri rab tsam ni bla yi /
NK131(do)005:2162: bdag med par 'dzin pa ni de lta ma yin no //
NK131(do)005:2165: stong pa nyid la lta nyes na //
NK131(do)005:2166: shes rab chung rnams phung 'gyur te //
NK131(do)005:2168: gang dag stong pa nyid lta ba //
NK131(do)005:2169: de dag sgrub tu med par gsungs //
NK131(do)005:2170: zhes pa rnams kyis gsal bar byas so //

NK131(do)005:2176: nas mnyam gzhag la rtog dpyod med ka med du

NK131(do)005:2178: bar gnas pa'i ngang du rtog dpyod kyang dgos par

NK131(do)005:2180: rgyu mtshan de rnams kyis rnam grangs pa'i stong nyid dang /
NK131(do)005:2181: blos byas kyi spros bral sogs la ming snyan pos
NK131(do)005:2182: ji ltar brjod kyang rnam par rtog pas bzhag pa
NK131(do)005:2183: tsam las don dam pa'i gnas lugs dang mtshan nyid
NK131(do)005:2184: ji lta ba'i sgom du mi btub pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)005:2186: gang zhig rang bzhin rang bzhin med //
NK131(do)005:2187: de ni brtags pa'i mtshan nyid yin //
NK131(do)005:2188: tshig dang sems kyi spyod yul rdzun //
NK131(do)005:2189: brdzun pa'i shes pas rnam brtags pa'i //
NK131(do)005:2190: mtha' gnyis su ni sems ltung bas //
NK131(do)005:2192: chos nyid ji lta ba mngon sum du mjal bar
NK131(do)005:2193: byed pa ni sgom byung rtog bral gyi shes rab
NK131(do)005:2194: nyid yin pas man ngag rig pa rnams kyis mnyam
NK131(do)005:2195: gzhag la dpyad sgom mi mdzad pa ni man ngag
NK131(do)005:2196: gi gnad gsang bla na med pa mkhyen pa yin
NK131(do)005:2197: la / kha cig 'phags pa'i mnyam gzhag la'ang rtog
NK131(do)005:2198: dpyod dgos par smra ba ni sangs rgyas pa'i lugs
NK131(do)005:2199: las gzhan du gyur pa ste nang pa'i grub mtha'
NK131(do)005:2200: smra ba tshad ldan thams cad kyis rnam rtog dngos
NK131(do)005:2201: gzhir dgos pa'i mnyam gzhag ma bshad pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)005:2202: rang sa'i shes rab kyis dpyod pa'i lhag mthong thams
NK131(do)005:2203: cad rjes thob tu mgrin gcig par smra ba'i phyir
NK131(do)005:2204: / khyad par theg chen ltar na man ngag snye
NK131(do)005:2205: ma las yan lag 'di rnams lam pa kho na'i
NK131(do)005:2206: / ste / lam la mnyam par bzhag pa la ni yang dag pa'i rtog pa dang /
NK131(do)005:2209: tshel ba dang dran pa rnams mi srid do //
NK131(do)005:2210: zhes 'phags pa'i mnyam gzhag la yang dag pa'i rtog
NK131(do)005:2211: dpyod kyang mi srid par bstan pa bzhin mdo rgyud
NK131(do)005:2212: thams cad nas mgrin gcig par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK131(do)005:2213: shes kyi mnyam par 'jog tshul kho na gsungs pa'i
NK131(do)005:2214: phyir ro // de bas na grub chen in+d+ra b+hu tis /
NK131(do)005:2215: ji srid ji srid rnam rtog pa //
NK131(do)005:2216: de srid thams cad kun nas rdzun //
NK131(do)005:2217: gang zhig de nyid ma brtags pa //
NK131(do)005:2218: de bzhin yang dag de bden pa //
NK131(do)005:2221: 'di ltar dus gsum rnam pa thams cad du //
NK131(do)005:2222: yid la byar med ma bcos gnyug ma'i ngang //
NK131(do)005:2223: de nyid skyong la sgom zhes tha snyad gdags //
NK131(do)005:2224: zhes pa 'dis ni bsam gtan mkhan po'i dgongs pa
NK131(do)005:2225: la shin tu 'jug cing tshad mar byed pa'i phyir
NK131(do)005:2226: ro // gzhan yang phyis kyi rtog ge pa mngon
NK131(do)005:2227: pa'i nga rgyal can 'ga' zhig gis rdzogs chen dang
NK131(do)005:2228: phyag chen gyi man ngag gi dgongs par /
NK131(do)005:2231: da ltar gyi shes pa bzo bcos med par rang babs su 'jog /
NK131(do)005:2232: ces 'byung ba 'di la dus gsum gyi yid kyi
NK131(do)005:2233: las bkag go snyam pas h+aa shang chen po'i phyogs
NK131(do)005:2234: su 'khrul pa'i rgyu yang rnam rtog thugs zhen gyis
NK131(do)005:2236: byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod las /
NK131(do)005:2237: de la 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa gang zhe na //
NK131(do)005:2238: gang 'das pa la sems mi 'jug pa dang /
NK131(do)005:2239: ma 'ongs pa la rnam par shes pa rjes su mi 'jug pa dang /
NK131(do)005:2240: da ltar byung ba la yid kyi byed pa mi 'jug pa ste /
NK131(do)005:2243: rnam par shes pa la mi gnas pas 'das pa la mi rtog /
NK131(do)005:2244: ma 'ongs pa la rlom sems su mi byed /
NK131(do)005:2245: da ltar byung ba la spros par mi byed /
NK131(do)005:2246: 'di ni dus gsum mnyam pa nyid 'khor gsum yongs
NK131(do)005:2247: su dag pa yin na sems can rnams kyi khong
NK131(do)005:2248: du ma chud pas de chud par bya'o //
NK131(do)005:2249: zhes sems can rnams la snying rje chen po 'jug go //
NK131(do)005:2250: zhes gsungs pas dus gsum gyi spros pa'i yid la
NK131(do)005:2251: byed pa thams cad dang bral ba'i de kho na
NK131(do)005:2252: nyid de gnyug ma'i sems nyid bzo bcos med pa'i
NK131(do)005:2253: gshis su mnyam par 'jog pa'i man ngag gi gnad
NK131(do)005:2254: gsang bla na med par bstan pa'i don mi gzhar
NK131(do)005:2255: ba la sems mnyam par bzhag pa nyid la bslab
NK131(do)005:2257: spyir yang h+aa shang bsam gtan mkhan po'i 'dod pa
NK131(do)005:2258: yin zer nas sgro 'dogs mang po tshig gi lam
NK131(do)005:2260: de'i gzhung lugs thams cad kyi mthun snang du grub
NK131(do)005:2261: pa zhig gzhir bzhag nas skyon rig pa'i sgo nas
NK131(do)005:2263: de ni bstan pa snga dar gyi skabs nas gter
NK131(do)005:2264: du sbas pa'i gtam rba bzhed du bkod pa ltar
NK131(do)005:2265: na phyis kyi smra ba po rnams kyis rba bzhed
NK131(do)005:2266: sogs su de'i bzhed pa yin rgyu pa 'ga' zhig
NK131(do)005:2267: phyogs sngar bkod pa la bskyar zlos mdzad pa rnams
NK131(do)005:2268: ni gya tshom tsam las ma 'das te dgag bya'i
NK131(do)005:2269: gzhung gang yin pa dngos su ma mthong phyin rba
NK131(do)005:2270: bzhed sogs su bkod pa de ni dpang po med
NK131(do)005:2271: pa'i thal mo ya gcig kho nar gyur pas so
NK131(do)005:2272: // de yang rba bzhed la khungs byed bzhin du /
NK131(do)005:2273: rgya nag mkhan po'i gzhung lugs kyi //
NK131(do)005:2274: yi ge tsam la brten nas kyang //
NK131(do)005:2275: de yi ming 'dogs gsang nas ni //
NK131(do)005:2276: phyag rgya chen por ming bsgyur nas //
NK131(do)005:2277: zhes pa la sogs gsungs pa 'dis ni rba bzhed
NK131(do)005:2278: nyid la'ang gnod pa bzlog dka' ste der rgya nag
NK131(do)005:2279: mkhan po'i gzhung lugs thams cad gter du sbas nas
NK131(do)005:2280: med zin par bshad na gzhung lugs de gang du
NK131(do)005:2281: byung / thog mar su'i lag tu byung zhes dris na smra bcad dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)005:2282: zhes thams cad mkhyen pa pad+ma dkar pos gsungs so //
NK131(do)005:2283: skabs de nyid kyi rgol ba po ka sh+ai dpon
NK131(do)005:2284: slob ni dbu ma rang rgyud par nges pa'i phyir
NK131(do)005:2285: / dbu ma'i mthar thug pa yang der ma nges shing /
NK131(do)005:2286: mnyam gzhag gi gnas skabs kun tu rtog dpyod mtha'
NK131(do)005:2287: gcig tu mi dgos ka med dbu ma pa mi
NK131(do)005:2288: bzhed de / 'phags mchog klu'i dgongs pa jo bo chen pos bkral ba las /
NK131(do)005:2289: dper na shing gnyis phan tshun drag tu drud pa
NK131(do)005:2290: las me byung ba'i rkyen gyis shing gnyis po tshig
NK131(do)005:2291: cing med pa'i rjes la gang gis sreg par byed
NK131(do)005:2292: pa'i me de nyid kyang rang zhi ba de bzhin
NK131(do)005:2293: du rang dang spyi'i mtshan gyi chos thams cad med
NK131(do)005:2294: par grub tsam na shes rab nyid snang ba med
NK131(do)005:2295: cing 'od gsal ba ci'i ngo bor ma grub pas
NK131(do)005:2296: / bying ba dang rgod pa la sogs pa'i skyon du gyur pa thams cad bsal te /
NK131(do)005:2297: bar skabs der shes pa cir yang mi rtog /
NK131(do)005:2298: cir yang mi 'dzin dran pa dang yid la byed
NK131(do)005:2299: pa thams cad spangs te zhes pa la sogs pa
NK131(do)005:2300: gsungs pa des sgom rim la gnod pa spangs dka'/
NK131(do)005:2301: gal te rang rgyud pa nyid gzhung 'dzugs tshe /
NK131(do)005:2303: nga la khas len med pas na //
NK131(do)005:2304: nga ni skyon med kho na yin //
NK131(do)005:2305: zhes pa 'di kha tsam gyis khas len bral ba'i
NK131(do)005:2306: lta ba ma yin par sems kyi ngo bo bsam
NK131(do)005:2307: brjod dang bral ba'i gshis kyi bzhugs tshul car phog
NK131(do)005:2308: tu ngo 'phrod pa'i tshe shes bya shes byed kyi
NK131(do)005:2309: spros pa thams cad zhi bar gyur pa la dgongs
NK131(do)005:2310: pa nges kyang chos nyid la lung ma bstan gyi
NK131(do)005:2312: smra bsam brjod med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK131(do)005:2313: zhes sgra gcan 'dzin gyis yum la bstod par /
NK131(do)005:2314: chos nyid yid la byar med pa'i don la brjod
NK131(do)005:2315: byar mdzad pa la'ang nongs pa de yod par 'gyur
NK131(do)005:2316: ro // des na gnas lugs don gyi dam pa'i
NK131(do)005:2317: bden pa chos nyid 'dus ma byas dge sdig spang
NK131(do)005:2318: blang gi bcing grol las 'das pa drang thad du
NK131(do)005:2319: ston pa'i skabs byas pa'i chos kyis phan ma btags
NK131(do)005:2320: ro // shing / sdig pas gnod pa ma bskyal bar gsungs pa ni /
NK131(do)005:2322: stong pa nyid la gzugs med /
NK131(do)005:2327: ces pa 'di la so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis spang bya la dor ba dang /
NK131(do)005:2328: blang byar ngos bzung ba'i chos gang yang mi dmigs shing /
NK131(do)005:2329: de bzhin du tshangs pa khyad par sems kyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK131(do)005:2330: gang yongs su dag pa 'di ni nam du yang yongs su ma dag par mi 'gyur te /
NK131(do)005:2331: yongs su dag pa gang gis rang bzhin gyis yongs
NK131(do)005:2332: su dag pa 'di ni shin tu yongs su dag
NK131(do)005:2333: pa ste / de'i phyir chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal zhes bya'o //
NK131(do)005:2334: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin de gang zhe na /
NK131(do)005:2335: chos thams cad ni stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin can te dmigs pa dang bral ba'o //
NK131(do)005:2336: chos thams cad ni mtshan ma med pa'i rang bzhin
NK131(do)005:2337: can te rtog pa dang rnam par rtog pa dang
NK131(do)005:2338: bral ba'o // chos thams cad ni smon pa med pa'i rang bzhin can te /
NK131(do)005:2343: shin tu ngo bo nyid dang bral ba yin te /
NK131(do)005:2344: de ni rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'o //
NK131(do)005:2345: zhes rnam par thar pa'i sgo gsum gyi mtshan nyid
NK131(do)005:2346: zab mo yang yid la mi byed pa'i don gyis
NK131(do)005:2347: blang dor gyi mtha' la zhen par mi bya ba'i
NK131(do)005:2348: don rjen par gtan la de las ci zhig phab
NK131(do)005:2349: / de dang gcig par dkon mchog brtsegs pa las kyang /
NK131(do)005:2350: dge ba'am mi dge ba'i chos la mngon par zhen par mi bya ste /
NK131(do)005:2351: dge ba'i chos rnams la mngon par zhen pas /
NK131(do)005:2352: mi dge ba'i chos rnams la mngon par zhen par 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)005:2353: mi dge ba'i chos rnams la mngon par zhen pas sdug bsngal dang /
NK131(do)005:2354: yid mi bde ba'i chos rnams mngon par 'byur bar
NK131(do)005:2355: 'gyur pa 'di dag ni sdug bsngal 'phags pa'i bden
NK131(do)005:2356: par btags pas de bzhin gshegs pas mi dge ba'i
NK131(do)005:2357: chos kyi rnam grangs su bstan to //
NK131(do)005:2358: dge ba dang mi dge ba la mngon par zhen pa med pa dang /
NK131(do)005:2359: sred pa 'gog pa 'di dag ni kun 'byung ba
NK131(do)005:2360: spang zhing 'phags pa'i bden pa gnyis po rtogs par
NK131(do)005:2361: bya ba'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pas dge ba'i chos
NK131(do)005:2362: kyi rnam grangs su bstan to //
NK131(do)005:2364: de la dge ba yang stong la /
NK131(do)005:2366: dge ba yang rnam par dben la /
NK131(do)005:2367: mi dge ba yang rnam par dben /
NK131(do)005:2368: dge ba yang mi dge ba dang rnam par mi 'dre la /
NK131(do)005:2369: mi dge ba yang dge ba dang mi 'dre zhing /
NK131(do)005:2370: dge ba dang mi dge bar mngon par zhen pa'i rgyu dang rkyen med do //
NK131(do)005:2371: zhes pa la sogs shin tu rgyas par gsungs pa yin no //
NK131(do)005:2372: des mtshon te don dam pa'i 'gog bden chos nyid
NK131(do)005:2373: gshis kyi bzhugs tshul lam bden 'dus byas kyis ma
NK131(do)005:2374: bcos pa drang thad du ston pa'i gsung rab thams
NK131(do)005:2377: sems nyid byang chub sems kyi ngo bo la //
NK131(do)005:2378: lta ba bsgom med spyod pa spyad du med //
NK131(do)005:2379: 'bras bu sgrub med sa lam bgrod du med //
NK131(do)005:2380: dkyil 'khor bskyed med bzlas brjod rdzogs rim med //
NK131(do)005:2381: dbang la bskur med dam tshig bsrung du med //
NK131(do)005:2382: ye nas lhun grub dag pa'i chos nyid la //
NK131(do)005:2383: glo bur rim rtsol rgyu 'bras chos las 'das //
NK131(do)005:2385: yo ga shin tu rnal 'byor rdzogs chen la //
NK131(do)005:2386: rgyu dang 'bras bu yod zer smra byed na //
NK131(do)005:2387: de ni rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i don mi ldan //
NK131(do)005:2388: don dam kun rdzob gnyis su smra byed na //
NK131(do)005:2389: sgro dang skur pa 'debs pa'i tshig yin te //
NK131(do)005:2390: de yis gnyis su med pa rtogs pa med //
NK131(do)005:2391: dus gsum sangs rgyas rnams kyi rtogs pa yang //
NK131(do)005:2392: gnyis su ma mthong rnam gzhag gcig tu rtogs //
NK131(do)005:2393: de skad bstan pa 'dis rdzogs chen pas thabs bsod
NK131(do)005:2394: nams kyi cha spangs pas h+aa shang gi chos lugs
NK131(do)005:2395: su 'gyur ro // zhes rtsod pa can du gtong
NK131(do)005:2396: 'dod pa'i phyi sa kyi mkhas rlom rtog ge pa
NK131(do)005:2397: dag mun nang gi mda' ltar rlom tshod du ma
NK131(do)005:2398: su 'gyur ro // song ba'am / phyogs chos ma
NK131(do)005:2399: grub pas brag cha'i sgra la dgag sgrub byed pa
NK131(do)005:2400: su 'gyur ro // song ba'am / dang mtshungs te
NK131(do)005:2401: / de ltar na spyod pa'i phyogs yal bar dor
NK131(do)005:2402: ba'i skyon de gzhan 'di thams cad la'ang 'jug par
NK131(do)005:2403: su 'gyur ro // song ba'am / dang mtshungs te / 'gyur te / kyee rdo rje las /
NK131(do)005:2404: bsgom med sgom pa po yang med //
NK131(do)005:2405: lha med sngags kyang yod ma yin //
NK131(do)005:2408: de la dkyil 'khor sbyin sreg med //
NK131(do)005:2409: gtor ma bzlas pa bgrang phreng dang //
NK131(do)005:2410: skyil mo krung dang stangs stabs sogs //
NK131(do)005:2411: spros bral rnam par bslu ba ste //
NK131(do)005:2412: bya ba ma yin dgag pa'ang min //
NK131(do)005:2414: bya ba rnams la rnal 'byor pa //
NK131(do)005:2415: lam chen dag tu yongs 'dzin la //
NK131(do)005:2416: ri dwags smig rgyu snyeg pa ltar //
NK131(do)005:2417: rtag tu snang yang mi zin no //
NK131(do)005:2420: ngo bo nyid la mnyam gnas na //
NK131(do)005:2421: dam tshig med cing sngags spyad med //
NK131(do)005:2422: rdo rje dril bu bzung mi dgos //
NK131(do)005:2424: zhes pa la sogs pa theg pa chen po'i mdo
NK131(do)005:2425: dang rgyud sde dgongs 'grel dang bcas pa rnams nas
NK131(do)005:2426: de skad bstan pas thams cad rtsod pa can du
NK131(do)005:2429: lung de rnams kyi dgongs pa ni lta ba'i ngo
NK131(do)005:2430: bo la dgongs pa yin mod spyod pa'i phyogs yal
NK131(do)005:2431: bar dor bas chog par bstan pa ma yin no
NK131(do)005:2433: 'di skad du rdo rje gtsug tor chen po'i mdo las /
NK131(do)005:2434: rdul snyed kyi bskal bar dam pa'i chos kyi mdo
NK131(do)005:2435: sde klog cing kha ton byed pa bas nyin gcig
NK131(do)005:2436: gam mtshan gcig zag pa med pa'i shes rab bsgom
NK131(do)005:2437: na bsod nams dpag tu med par che'o //
NK131(do)005:2438: de ci'i phyir zhe na skye shing las ring du gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)005:2439: zhes gsungs pa'i don la dgongs pas /
NK131(do)005:2440: h+aa shang chen pos kyang chos nyid kyi don la
NK131(do)005:2441: mnyam gzhag gtso bor byed pa'i gnas skabs su de
NK131(do)005:2442: nyid kyi gegs su 'gyur ba dang 'dus byas bsod
NK131(do)005:2443: nams kyi mtha' la zhen na 'dus ma byas kyi
NK131(do)005:2444: chos nyid la dmigs pa can gyis sgrib par 'gyur
NK131(do)005:2445: ba dgongs nas de ltar bstan pa las /
NK131(do)005:2446: mnyam par bzhag pa mi dgos la /
NK131(do)005:2447: spyod pa phyogs kyang yal bar dor bas chog go //
NK131(do)005:2448: zhes ma bstan pa'i phyir dang /
NK131(do)005:2449: de tsam zhig gis bsod nams kyi tshogs yal bar 'dod bar yang mi 'grub ste /
NK131(do)005:2451: de kho na nyid kyi lta ba'i gnas lugs de
NK131(do)005:2452: ma mnyam par 'jog pa na byang chub phyogs kyi
NK131(do)005:2453: spyod pa'i chos thams cad kyang rang bzhin gyis tshang
NK131(do)005:2454: ba'i tshul bsam gtan mkhan pos 'di skad du /
NK131(do)005:2455: 'dzin pa ma mchis na sbyin pa sogs zag pa
NK131(do)005:2456: med pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa drug mnyam par
NK131(do)005:2457: bzhag pa'i rang ngo la sgra ji bzhin pa tshang
NK131(do)005:2459: de la gzhan dag na re /
NK131(do)005:2460: bsam gtan mkhan pos chos de dang de'i gnad bcos par 'gyur bas mi 'thad de /
NK131(do)005:2461: de ltar na sbyin sogs pha rol phyin pa drug
NK131(do)005:2462: po'ang bstan pa don med par 'gyur te mnyam par
NK131(do)005:2463: bzhag pa kho nas de rnams kyi go chod pa'i
NK131(do)005:2464: phyir ro // zhes smra ba ni nyes pa chen po ste /
NK131(do)005:2465: sbyin pa la sogs thabs kyi cha de rnams ye
NK131(do)005:2466: shes rtogs pa'i grogs sam thabs su 'gyur ba'i phyir
NK131(do)005:2467: / yan lag 'di dag thams cad ni /
NK131(do)005:2468: thub pas shes rab don du gsungs //
NK131(do)005:2469: zhes bshad cing shes rab kyis ma zin pa'i sbyin
NK131(do)005:2470: pa la sogs thabs kyi tshogs ci tsam rgya che
NK131(do)005:2471: yang 'jig rten pa'am tshu rol las mi 'da' bas
NK131(do)005:2472: 'khor ba'i bde 'bras tsam du 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK131(do)005:2474: dmus long dmigs bu med pa bye ba khrag khrig rnams //
NK131(do)005:2475: lam yang mi shes grong khyer 'jug par ga la 'gyur //
NK131(do)005:2476: shes rab med na mig med pha rol phyin lnga 'di //
NK131(do)005:2477: dmigs bu med pas byang chub reg par nus ma yin //
NK131(do)005:2478: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir sbyin pa la sogs bsod nams
NK131(do)005:2479: kyi cha rang ga ba rnams la shes rab kyis
NK131(do)005:2480: ma zin pas 'dus ma byas kyi dge rtsa mi
NK131(do)005:2481: gnas la / de med pas mya ngan las 'das pa'i rgyur mi 'gyur zhing /
NK131(do)005:2482: shes rab la ni 'dus ma byas kyi dge ba
NK131(do)005:2483: gdod nas lhun grub tu yod pa'i phyir bsod nams
NK131(do)005:2484: kyi cha sbyin pa la sogs pa rnams kyang rang
NK131(do)005:2485: bzhin gyis tshang ba yin te /
NK131(do)005:2486: rdo rje ting nge 'dzin gyi mdo las /
NK131(do)005:2487: sems stong pa nyid du mi g.yo na pha rol tu phyin pa drug 'dus so //
NK131(do)005:2489: tshangs pa khyad par sems kyis zhus pa theg pa chen po'i mdo sde las /
NK131(do)005:2490: mngon par 'du mi byed pa'i tshul gyis tshul khrims kyis mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK131(do)005:2491: skad cig pa'i tshul gyis bzod pas mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK131(do)005:2492: blang ba dang dor ba med pa'i tshul gyis brtson 'grus kyis mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK131(do)005:2493: rnam par mi rtog pa'i tshul gyis bsam gtan gyis mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK131(do)005:2494: thogs pa med pa'i tshul gyis shes rab kyis mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK131(do)005:2501: mi dmigs pa shes rab bo //
NK131(do)005:2503: de bzhin du rdzogs chen pas kyang gshis la bya
NK131(do)005:2504: ba dang bral ba'i gnas lugs su mnyam par 'jog
NK131(do)005:2505: pa de la lam bden gyi chos thams cad ma
NK131(do)005:2506: rtsol bzhin du tshang bar bzhed pa ste /
NK131(do)005:2508: don gyi snying po rnal ma byar med la //
NK131(do)005:2509: rnal 'byor chen po rnams kyis mthong ba ni //
NK131(do)005:2510: ye nas rang rgyud dag pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK131(do)005:2511: rgyu las bdag nyid lha yi dkyil 'khor de //
NK131(do)005:2512: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi yis rdzogs byas te //
NK131(do)005:2513: 'phro 'du'i bdag nyid lhun gyis grub par gnas //
NK131(do)005:2516: spros pa med pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK131(do)005:2517: lha dang sngags ni rnam par gnas //
NK131(do)005:2518: zhes pa la sogs pa'i theg pa chen po'i mdo
NK131(do)005:2519: dang rgyud sde thams cad kyis zab mo'i de kho
NK131(do)005:2520: na nyid ston tshul gcig tu nges pa'i phyir ro
NK131(do)005:2521: // yang 'di skad du gser gyi thur ma pas /
NK131(do)005:2522: kun byed rgyal po de lta ba'i ldog pa nas yang dag pa yin kyang /
NK131(do)005:2523: chos de'i rgyud 'dzin rnams kyis spyod pa'i phyogs dang mi sbyor zhing /
NK131(do)005:2524: spyod pa yal bar dor bas chog pa'i grub mtha' dang /
NK131(do)005:2525: lag len du byed na rgya nag mkhan po'i chos lugs su song /
NK131(do)005:2526: zhes pa bstan bcos 'di'i bzhed pa nyid du nges so //
NK131(do)005:2528: spyir skyon de gzugs brnyan spangs pa'i grib mar gyur la /
NK131(do)005:2529: bye brag rdzogs chen du chos nyid gshis kyi bzhugs
NK131(do)005:2530: tshul drang thad du bstan pa tsam gyis der 'gyur
NK131(do)005:2531: na gong du drangs pa'i theg pa chen po'i zab
NK131(do)005:2532: don ston pa'i mdo dang rgyud sde thams cad kyang
NK131(do)005:2534: rdzogs chen pas ni kun byed kyi lung gong du drangs ma thag pa de bzhin dang /
NK131(do)005:2535: der ma zad rdzogs pa chen po rdo la gser zhun du /
NK131(do)005:2536: bder gshegs ma lus yum du gyur pas rgyal ba kun gyi lam gcig pu /
NK131(do)005:2537: tshul khrims la sogs pha rol phyin lam spyod pa rgya mtsho'i gzhir gyur pa /
NK131(do)005:2538: zhes pa la sogs rgyas par gsungs pa'i grub matha'i
NK131(do)005:2539: 'cha' lugs chen po 'di la tshad mar byed cing
NK131(do)005:2540: lag len du 'debs pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)005:2541: spyir 'di lta bu'i 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid la
NK131(do)005:2542: dgongs pa'i rgyu 'bras la zlo ba'i rdo rje'i gsang
NK131(do)005:2543: tshig rmad du byung ba rnams kyi brjod bya gnas
NK131(do)005:2544: lugs blang dor med pa'i don la yid ches pa
NK131(do)005:2545: ni phyir mi ldog pa'i skal ldan gyi tshad du
NK131(do)005:2546: zab mo'i mdo sde rnams las gsungs te /
NK131(do)005:2547: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK131(do)005:2550: byang chub sems dpa' las dang po la chos ji ltar ston dris pa'i lan du /
NK131(do)005:2553: gti mug ma sel cig /'jig tshogs las gyen du ma skyod cig sogs nas /
NK131(do)005:2554: sangs rgyas yin la ma byed cig /
NK131(do)005:2556: dge 'dun la mchod pa ma byed cig /
NK131(do)005:2557: bslab pa dag ma len cig /
NK131(do)005:2558: srid pa nye bar zhi ba don du ma gnyer cig /
NK131(do)005:2559: chu bo las ma rgal cig /
NK131(do)005:2560: ces gdams ngag 'di lta bu 'di las dang po pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la gdams par bya /
NK131(do)005:2563: chos thams cad kyi chos nyid mi gnas pa kho na yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)005:2564: byis pa de dag ni skye ba dang 'gag pa'i chos su lung ston par byed do //
NK131(do)005:2565: chos kyi dbyings 'di ni rnam par mi rtog pas phye ba yin te /
NK131(do)005:2566: chos 'di rnams kyi rang bzhin ltar rjes su rtogs pa yang yin pa de ni byang chub bo //
NK131(do)005:2567: zhes de ltar gdams na gal te mi skrag mi
NK131(do)005:2568: dngangs shing dngangs par mi 'gyur na e ma byang
NK131(do)005:2569: chub sems dpa' 'di ni phyir mi ldog pa ste
NK131(do)005:2570: phyir mi ldog pa'i sa'i skal ba can yin no
NK131(do)005:2571: snyam du shes par bya ste gdams ngag 'dis yang
NK131(do)005:2572: nas yang du dga' ba bskyed par bya'o //
NK131(do)005:2573: zhes smras par gsungs pa'i phyir phyi ma'i dus su
NK131(do)005:2574: zab mo'i mthar thug gang yin pa la blo gros
NK131(do)005:2575: ma phyogs shing tshig gis theg pa chen po la
NK131(do)005:2576: skad du byed par bsam sbyor byis pa rtog ge
NK131(do)005:2577: la rnam par byang ba tsam gyis don dam pa'i
NK131(do)005:2578: bden pa 'dus ma byas kyi bzhugs tshul 'di lta
NK131(do)005:2579: bu thos na yid mi ches shing rna ba 'gebs
NK131(do)005:2580: pa tsam du byed pa ni chos nyid de /
NK131(do)005:2581: dpal 'dzin gyis rdzogs pa chen po'i chos skad la bsams nas khyad par h+aa shang grub mtha' dang /
NK131(do)005:2582: man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba bsres //
NK131(do)005:2583: zhes pa sogs smra ba bzhin no 'dis ni nges
NK131(do)005:2584: don gyi mdo dang rgyud sde rnams la tshig klog
NK131(do)005:2586: myong yang phyogs lhung gi 'og nas ldang bar ma
NK131(do)005:2587: nus pas rtsa ltung drug pa'i khur mkhyen bzhin du
NK131(do)005:2589: hwa shang chen po'i chos kyi khungs gang yin gyi
NK131(do)005:2590: gtam tsam yang snyan gyi bu gar ltung ma myong
NK131(do)005:2591: bzhin du rdzogs pa chen po rtsod pa can du
NK131(do)005:2592: gtong ba bzhed pa kho nas lugs de ngan pa
NK131(do)005:2593: zhig yin du yod bsam pa ste phyogs rgyug gi
NK131(do)005:2594: gtam 'di 'dra ba la yid brtan gang yang med
NK131(do)005:2595: cing 'di tsam gyis kyang mtshang brtol ba sla bas
NK131(do)005:2596: shags 'byed kyi yul du ma dmigs so //
NK131(do)005:2597: de lta mod kyi chos nyid zab mo'i gnas la
NK131(do)005:2598: the tshom tsam skyes pas kyang mthar phan yon chen
NK131(do)005:2599: po thob pa ni yin te /
NK131(do)005:2601: bsod nams chung bas chos 'di la //
NK131(do)005:2602: the tshom tsam yang mi skye ste //
NK131(do)005:2603: 'di la the tshom skyes pas kyang //
NK131(do)005:2604: srid pa hrul bor byed par 'gyur //
NK131(do)005:2606: khye'u rin chen byin gyis 'jam dpal la gong du
NK131(do)005:2607: drangs pa'i blang dor med pa'i don smras pa'i tshe
NK131(do)005:2608: dmigs pa can gyi dge slong brgyad ma mos pas
NK131(do)005:2609: de dag khrag dron mo skyugs te shi nas dmyal
NK131(do)005:2612: dge slong de dag gis zab mo'i chos som nyi
NK131(do)005:2613: dang bcas pas thos pa'i mthus de kho nar dmyal
NK131(do)005:2614: ba las thar te dga' ldan gyi lhar skye zhing
NK131(do)005:2615: / bskal pa drug cu rtsa brgyad du sangs rgyas
NK131(do)005:2616: khrag khrig bcu ma nyes par byas nas gdod 'tshang
NK131(do)005:2617: rgya bar lung bstan pa'i tshul 'byung ba dang /
NK131(do)005:2619: zab mo'i chos la ma mos pa'i dge slong brgya
NK131(do)005:2620: dmyal bar ltungs pa chos de thos pa tsam gyis
NK131(do)005:2621: mod la dga' ldan gyi lhar skyes shing phyis nas
NK131(do)005:2622: byams pa'i 'khor du dgra bcom pa thob par lung
NK131(do)005:2623: bstan pa sogs theg pa chen po'i mdo sde rnams
NK131(do)005:2624: su mang du 'byung ba ltar nges pas so //
NK131(do)005:2626: kha cig 'bras bu'i mthar thug ni //
NK131(do)005:2627: 'od gsal yin zhes smra ba thos //
NK131(do)005:2629: bla med kyi rgyud sde'i rim pa lnga pa dang /
NK131(do)005:2630: sbyor ba yan lag drug pa ba sogs kyis 'od
NK131(do)005:2631: gsal la mthar thug tu bzhed pa nges dgongs pa
NK131(do)005:2632: yin no // rdzogs chen pas lhun grub thod rgal
NK131(do)005:2633: gyi lam 'od gsal la mthar thug tu bzhed pa
NK131(do)005:2634: yin no // ni / 'di nyams len mthar phyin pa zhig gis /
NK131(do)005:2635: phyi 'byung zhing khams su grol nas longs sku'i zhing
NK131(do)005:2636: gi yon tan da lta mngon du byed pa dang
NK131(do)005:2637: / nang 'byung 'od gsal du dngas pas snang gzugs yod la /
NK131(do)005:2638: reg gzugs med pas 'khor ba ma stongs par rtag
NK131(do)005:2639: khyab lhun grub kyi phrin las kyis gdul bya'i don
NK131(do)005:2640: mdzad pa pad 'byung dang bi ma la ltar chos
NK131(do)005:2641: zad 'pho ba chen po'i sku bsgrub tu yod pa'i
NK131(do)005:2642: phyir zab pa dang rgya che ba'i khyad par bsam
NK131(do)005:2643: gyis mi khyab pa'i snying thig gi gsang ba ngo
NK131(do)005:2644: mtshar ba rnams spro bar byar yod kyang brjod pa'i
NK131(do)005:2645: skabs su ma babs pas shes par 'dod pa srid
NK131(do)005:2646: na kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po klong chen pa'i
NK131(do)005:2647: gsungs rab spyi dang bye brag rnams su gsal lo
NK131(do)005:2649: gter nas byung ba'i glegs bam dang //
NK131(do)005:2650: gzhan nas brkus pa'i chos lugs dang //
NK131(do)005:2651: brtsams chos dang ni rmi lam chos //
NK131(do)005:2652: blo bzung ma yi chos lugs la //
NK131(do)005:2653: rdo rje 'chang la brgyud pa snyeg /
NK131(do)005:2654: ces gsungs pa dgag bya dang dgos pa'i skabs mi
NK131(do)005:2655: byed pa'i mkhas su re ba rnams kyis tshig 'di
NK131(do)005:2656: drang thad du dpyad na mi legs te /
NK131(do)005:2658: bstan pa'i gnad bcos pa'i so skye blun pos de ltar sbyar ba la dgongs pa yin mchi /
NK131(do)005:2659: mchog gzigs rnams la gsungs par ni rnam pa kun tu bsam par mi bya ste /
NK131(do)005:2660: grub brnyes rnams la dag pa'i snang bar dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'am /
NK131(do)005:2661: rdo rje phag mo sogs lhag pa'i lha dang /
NK131(do)005:2662: rdo rje 'dzin pa rnams kyis zhal bstan zhing phal cher la dbang bskur /
NK131(do)005:2665: 'ga' zhig la don brgyud kyi dgongs pa'i byin rlabs 'pho bar mdzad /
NK131(do)005:2666: glegs bam sogs lung bstan dang rjes su gnang ba
NK131(do)005:2667: byin pa tsam gyis chos de dang de'i don gyi
NK131(do)005:2668: brgyud pa bzhugs pas rtsod pa med pas de la
NK131(do)005:2669: chos dang mthun pa'i glan ka mi 'jug ste /
NK131(do)005:2670: sangs rgyas kyi byin rlabs dang rjes su gnang ba
NK131(do)005:2671: thob pa rnams bka' dngos dang mtshungs par rgya bod
NK131(do)005:2672: gnyis kar yongs su grags pas kho bo cag gis
NK131(do)005:2673: grub zin bsgrub pas ci bya ste /
NK131(do)005:2675: 'dus pa 'phags skor rnams zla grags la mgon po
NK131(do)005:2676: klu sgrub kyis gsungs par 'dod pa ni ye shes
NK131(do)005:2677: kyi sku las nos par byed dgos /
NK131(do)005:2678: gzugs sku ni de dus mi bzhugs shing /
NK131(do)005:2679: de bzhin du gdol ba'i bu ma tang+gi pas sgron
NK131(do)005:2680: gsal gyi glegs bam rnyed nas rgyud kyi bka' srol
NK131(do)005:2681: byung ba dang / rol pa'i rdo rjes rtog bdun
NK131(do)005:2682: o rgyan nas spyan drangs pa rnams kyang de lta
NK131(do)005:2684: de bzhin du sa ra has sangs rgyas thod pa dang /
NK131(do)005:2685: ma h+aa m+aa y+aa'i rgyud rnams o rgyan gyi yul nas ku ku ri pas drangs pa dang /
NK131(do)005:2686: zhi byed kyi rgyud rnams dur khrod dpal gyi rgyu
NK131(do)005:2687: skar rol pa nas pha dam pas spyan drangs pa
NK131(do)005:2688: sogs / rgyud sde so so'i srol 'byed kyi grub
NK131(do)005:2689: thob de rnams la lhag pa'i lhas snang bar mdzad
NK131(do)005:2690: pa kho na mang ba'i phyir dang /
NK131(do)005:2691: gangs can gyi ljongs su'ang dag snang gi chos bka'
NK131(do)005:2692: rgya gar slob dpon rnams nas brgyud pa'i rnam grangs
NK131(do)005:2693: mang po dang / bod kyi mkhas grub rnams nyid la'ang zhal gzigs dag snang dang /
NK131(do)005:2694: snyan rgyud kyi chos skor ji snyed cig bzhugs pa
NK131(do)005:2695: rnams kyang de dag dang mtshungs pa'i phyir rtsod med
NK131(do)005:2697: des na gter zhes bya ba'i go ba ni /
NK131(do)005:2700: 'gro lding sogs yul chen yul phran so so nas
NK131(do)005:2701: byung ba'i rgyud sde'i glegs bam rnams gdul bya dus
NK131(do)005:2702: la ma babs bar mkha' 'gro'i gsang mdzod rnams su
NK131(do)005:2703: gter du bzhugs pa dus la babs nas skal ba
NK131(do)005:2704: dang ldan pa'i grub thob rnams la lha dang bla
NK131(do)005:2705: mas lung bstan nas rnyed pa'am spyan drangs te snod
NK131(do)005:2706: ldan nyung shas la rim gyis spel nas dngos grub
NK131(do)005:2707: thob pa ste / de dang mtshungs par slob dpon pad+ma dang /
NK131(do)005:2708: chos rgyal srong btsan sgam po sogs grub thob rnams
NK131(do)005:2709: kyis gter du sbas pa'i chos kyang sprul pa'i rje
NK131(do)005:2710: 'bangs rnams la sngon du smon lam gtad rgya'i dbang
NK131(do)005:2711: bskur nas phyi ma'i tshe 'gro don dus la babs
NK131(do)005:2712: na sngon gyi smon lam mtha' btsan pas rje 'bangs
NK131(do)005:2713: de dag gi sprul pa rnams la slar yang ye
NK131(do)005:2714: shes kyi skus dbang bskur lung bstan gyis rjes su
NK131(do)005:2715: bzung nas rang skal dus bab kyi gter 'don par
NK131(do)005:2716: mdzad nas gdul bya'i don rlabs po che sgrub pa
NK131(do)005:2717: ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i phrin las chud mi gsan
NK131(do)005:2718: pa'i thabs la mkhas pa'i phrin las phyogs gcig yin
NK131(do)005:2719: la / khyad par ye shes kyi sku ni rnam smin las ches lhag cing /
NK131(do)005:2720: mtshan ma'i dkyil 'khor las ye shes nus pa lhag pa dang /
NK131(do)005:2721: spros bcas kyi dbang las ye shes 'pho ba'i dbang
NK131(do)005:2722: bskur khyad par du 'phags pa snod bcud gnyis ka'i
NK131(do)005:2723: rten 'brel las gsang sngags thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK131(do)005:2724: zab gnad du shes par bya dgos pa nyid do
NK131(do)005:2725: // bye brag phyir mi ldog pa'i byang chub sems
NK131(do)005:2726: dpa' la chos kyi gter chen po 'byung ba ni
NK131(do)005:2727: sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'i 'dul ba la snang /
NK131(do)005:2729: mngon pa'i chos nyid dang mi 'gal te /
NK131(do)005:2730: 'phags pa bsod nams thams cad sdud pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi mdo las /
NK131(do)005:2731: dri ma med pa'i gzi brjid chos 'dod pa'i byang
NK131(do)005:2732: chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po bsam pa phun
NK131(do)005:2733: sum tshogs pa gus pa dang bcas pa rnams ni
NK131(do)005:2734: 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan na 'dug kyang sangs rgyas
NK131(do)005:2735: bcom ldan 'das rnams zhal ston par mdzad cing chos
NK131(do)005:2737: dri ma med pa'i gzi brjid chos 'dod pa'i byang
NK131(do)005:2738: chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams kyis chos
NK131(do)005:2740: shing dag gi nang du bcug pa dag yod de /
NK131(do)005:2741: gzungs dang chos kyi sgo mtha' yas pa glegs bam
NK131(do)005:2742: du byas pa dag kyang lag tu 'ong bar 'gyur
NK131(do)005:2743: ro // dri ma med pa'i gzi brjid chos 'dod
NK131(do)005:2744: pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams
NK131(do)005:2745: la ni sngon sangs rgyas mthong ba'i lha rnams kyis
NK131(do)005:2746: spobs pa sgrub par byed do //
NK131(do)005:2747: dri ma med pa'i gzi brjid chos 'dod pa'i byang
NK131(do)005:2748: chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams ni tshe
NK131(do)005:2749: zad na'ang sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams dang lha
NK131(do)005:2750: rnams kyis tshe dang stobs sgrub par byed do //
NK131(do)005:2751: sangs rgyas kyi byin rlabs dang /
NK131(do)005:2752: lha'i byin rlabs kyis de dag 'dod na lo stong du'ang 'khod do //
NK131(do)005:2754: dpal mchog gi rgyud las kyang //
NK131(do)005:2755: rgyud dang rgyud kyi rgyal po gang //
NK131(do)005:2756: phyag na rdo rje khyod nyid kyis //
NK131(do)005:2757: gter nas gter du phyung zhing stsal //
NK131(do)005:2760: phyi ma de tshe dus dag tu //
NK131(do)005:2761: dge slong dgra bcom zhes bya ba //
NK131(do)005:2763: sngon gyi ngas ni gang bshad pa //
NK131(do)005:2764: theg pa chen po'i mdo sde yang //
NK131(do)005:2765: de yi tshe na bum pa las //
NK131(do)005:2766: dkar thub chen pos 'dren par byed //
NK131(do)005:2767: glegs bam de la de bltas nas //
NK131(do)005:2768: de la sngags ni zlos pa ni //
NK131(do)005:2769: zhes lung bstan pa bzhin dge slong dgra bcom par
NK131(do)005:2770: grags pas bum pa bzang po zhig nas mdo la
NK131(do)005:2771: sogs pa'i chos gang 'dod kyi gter bton nas nyams
NK131(do)005:2772: su blangs pa'i lo rgyus 'byung ba dang /
NK131(do)005:2773: mdo sde mdzangs blun du khyim bdag zhig gi khyim
NK131(do)005:2774: gyi ka ba nas bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad pa'i
NK131(do)005:2775: cho ga thon pa'i lo rgyus kyang snang ba'i phyir
NK131(do)005:2776: gter gyi tshad ma de las ci zhig dgos /
NK131(do)005:2777: sangs rgyas kyi zhal bstan cing byin gyis brlabs pa'i phyir brgyud pa de ltar drangs bas ci sto /
NK131(do)005:2780: nye brgyud dang ring brgyud kyi khyad par bshad pa thams cad la de dang mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)005:2781: yang phyis kyi mkhas rlom 'ga' zhig gis gter chos
NK131(do)005:2782: dang gter ston rnying ma 'ba' zhig las gzhan la
NK131(do)005:2783: ma grags snyam du sdang zhugs byed pa ni rang
NK131(do)005:2784: nyid thos pa chung ba'i mngon rtags bstan pa dang
NK131(do)005:2785: lhan cig chos spang ba la zhugs pa ste 'phags
NK131(do)005:2786: yul gyi grub thob gong du smras pa de dag
NK131(do)005:2788: rje mar pas rdo rje gdan nas rdzogs rim rlung sems dbyer med bton pa dang /
NK131(do)005:2789: bla ma rdo rje gdan pa dang ba ri lo
NK131(do)005:2790: ts+aa bas seng gdong ma'i sgrub skor rdo rje gdan
NK131(do)005:2791: gyi shar phyogs pha bong g.yag 'dra ba'i 'og nas
NK131(do)005:2792: bton pa dang / ku ru kul+le'i sgrub skor 'ba'
NK131(do)005:2793: zhig rdo rje gdan gyi byang phyogs lha mo dud
NK131(do)005:2794: sol ma'i nu 'bur na yod pa sgrol mas lung
NK131(do)005:2795: bstan te bla ma gnyan lo ts+aa sa bton pa
NK131(do)005:2796: bton pa dang / dang / lha sa'i dkar chag
NK131(do)005:2797: ka ba bum pa can nas jo bo a ti
NK131(do)005:2799: phan gnod las tshogs kyi skor 'ga' zhig ka ba shing lo can /
NK131(do)005:2801: seng mgo can rnams na yod pa bla ma zhang
NK131(do)005:2802: dang jo gdan dkon mchog grags gnyis kyis phal cher
NK131(do)005:2803: bton pa dang / ro snyoms skor drug ti phu
NK131(do)005:2804: pas lung bstan bzhin rje btsun ras chung pas lho
NK131(do)005:2805: brag mkhar chur sbas pa phyis su 'gro mgon gtsang
NK131(do)005:2806: pa rgya ras kyis gter nas bton pa dang /
NK131(do)005:2807: sems khrid yid bzhin nor bu rje dwags po rin po che dang /
NK131(do)005:2808: skyes bu ye shes rdo rje dpon slob kyis mtsho
NK131(do)005:2809: man+dala nag po la gter du sbas pa 'gro mgon
NK131(do)005:2810: dung mtsho ras pas gter nas bton pa dang /
NK131(do)005:2811: rnam sras kyi sgrub skor 'ga' zhig bya rgod gshongs
NK131(do)005:2812: nas gnyal ba nyi ma shes rab kyis bton pa
NK131(do)005:2813: dang / pu tra ming sring gi sgrub skor bsam
NK131(do)005:2814: yas nas lha btsun byang chub 'od kyis bton pa
NK131(do)005:2815: sogs rnying ma kho nar ma zad rgya gar dang
NK131(do)005:2816: bod kyi grub mtha' thams cad la yod /
NK131(do)005:2817: ma cig lab sgron gyi gdams pa gcod kyi skor
NK131(do)005:2818: rnams ma gcig nyid kyis gter du sbas pa kun
NK131(do)005:2819: spangs brtson 'grus seng ges bton pa dang /
NK131(do)005:2821: srad rgyud kyi mgon khang du 'dul nag pa dpal
NK131(do)005:2822: ldan bzang pos gter du sbas pa'i chos rgyal gyi
NK131(do)005:2823: las tshogs 'ga' zhig rgyud chen sangs rgyas rgya mtshos
NK131(do)005:2824: bton pa dang / 'jam dbyangs bzhad pas gter lung
NK131(do)005:2825: zhes pa'i sa cha nas ma gcig gi lung bstan
NK131(do)005:2826: dang dung dkar sogs rdzas 'ga' re bton zhes zer
NK131(do)005:2827: bton pa dang / ba dang / dga' ldan khri pa ngag dbang mchog ldan gyi mnal lam du /
NK131(do)005:2828: rje tsong kha pa dgung lo bco lnga bzhes pa'i
NK131(do)005:2829: tshod tsam pa brgyangs bzang po'i na bza' gsol ba
NK131(do)005:2830: zhig gis bya khyung dgon pa'i mchod rten steng na
NK131(do)005:2831: gter 'ga' zhig 'don rgyu yod tshul lung bstan na'ang
NK131(do)005:2832: khri pa de nyid khams su phebs rgyu ma byung
NK131(do)005:2833: bas / gter 'don rgyu ngo ma thogs pa sogs
NK131(do)005:2834: gter gyi sgros mang bas gter chos yin tshad rnying
NK131(do)005:2835: ma dang gter ston yin tshad zog par khas blangs
NK131(do)005:2836: phyin ha cang thal ba 'dra snyam mo //
NK131(do)005:2838: 'gro la phan bzhed rgyal bas gdul bya yi //
NK131(do)005:2839: khams dbang bsam pa dang mthun bstan pa la //
NK131(do)005:2840: blo mchog rnams dang dbyer med chos kyi rjes //
NK131(do)005:2841: byi dor mdzad pa bstan la ri mor che //
NK131(do)005:2842: 'on tang phyi dus log lta'i rab rib kyis //
NK131(do)005:2843: chos mig ldongs pas ngan shags lhur len la //
NK131(do)005:2844: zhugs rnams thub bstan dkrugs pa'i rgyab rten du //
NK131(do)005:2845: 'khyer bas gzhung 'di dri ma can du byas //
NK131(do)005:2846: dgag dgos dpyad pa blo mig ma zums pas //
NK131(do)005:2847: chos rje'i dgongs pa gang yin rma med du //
NK131(do)005:2848: legs par 'dogs pa'i gser thur 'di thogs phyin //
NK131(do)005:2849: yang dag gnas la sgrib phyed ma bcad dam //
NK131(do)005:2850: sngon rabs mkhas gzhung rnams kyang r+ts+wa ltar du //
NK131(do)005:2851: 'dor na bdag 'dra'i nyi tshe'i tshig gis ci //
NK131(do)005:2852: sgog pa'i dri bzhin lhan skyes log lta'i blo //
NK131(do)005:2853: gtong ba mi byed de la ci byar yod //
NK131(do)005:2854: ma rtogs log rtog kun nas dkris pa yis //
NK131(do)005:2855: nyes gyur ma lus dbang gyur rnams kyi drung //
NK131(do)005:2856: mthol bshags dge bas 'gro rnams ston pa bzhi'i //
NK131(do)005:2857: chos rab 'byed la 'phags rnams nyid ltar shog /
NK131(do)005:2858: nam zhig mngon dag'i zhing du chos kyi rje //
NK131(do)005:2859: rdzogs sangs rgyas mdun 'phags pa'i 'khor tshogs dang //
NK131(do)005:2860: lhan cig thugs kyi gsar ba 'dzin byed cing //
NK131(do)005:2861: yang dag lam du 'gro kun sgrol nus shog //
NK131(do)005:2862: de ltar na ri kha ba can gyi khongs su
NK131(do)005:2863: bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa rin po che'i snang
NK131(do)005:2864: byed gcig pu lta bur 'gyur pa chos kyi rje
NK131(do)005:2865: sa skya pan+di ta chen pos sdom pa gsum gyi
NK131(do)005:2866: rab tu dbye ba'i bstan bcos chen por rgyal bstan
NK131(do)005:2867: shing rta chen po'i ring lugs rma med pa la
NK131(do)005:2868: drang ba'i phyir du dgongs nas /
NK131(do)005:2869: bka' stsal ba'i dngos bstan tshig kha shas la brten
NK131(do)005:2870: nas tshig la rtog pa'i mkhas par rlom pa dang
NK131(do)005:2871: / blun po dag gis ma rtogs pa'am /
NK131(do)005:2872: rtogs kyang phyogs lhung gis kun nas dkris pas rang
NK131(do)005:2873: dang skal dman du ma chos spong ba la sbyor
NK131(do)005:2874: ba mthong bas de dag la cung zad phan du
NK131(do)005:2875: re na gzu bo'i blos drang shan 'byed pa'i yi
NK131(do)005:2876: ge 'di nyid snga mo zhig nas sbyar ba la
NK131(do)005:2877: / slar yang tshig don gyi cha la zhus dag
NK131(do)005:2878: gis phri bstan cung zad dang bcas chos rje rgyal
NK131(do)005:2879: ba kahthoga pa yab sras kyi gdul bya'i rjes zhugs
NK131(do)005:2880: su rlom pas rig pa 'dzin pa tshe dbang mchog
NK131(do)005:2881: grub nges don bstan 'phel dpal bzang por sgro btags
NK131(do)005:2882: pas dpal kah thog rdo rje gdan gyi g+han+d+ho la'i
NK131(do)005:2883: ba gam du bris pa re zhig rdzogs so //
